ry-title'> Le gâteau nantais </h3> <div class='post-body-container'> <div class='post-body entry-content float-container' id='post-body-4089170631950631178'> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"> <a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiaw0PdYAI0Z6Qz2a5zA6U9IBFvwUNpjEe9tZ50Cx9DSgoTZMfmk8SEIWEyxd815kIUbs2H7dhyphenhyphenlUzfAe4yXGPB79fJiG0AXIPcw7BQKZdPyKGXlGERrx0Fn-wyoM3bdWddSftWAIqqHNH5/s1600/DSC05672.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"Le gâteau nantais\" border=\"0\" height=\"581\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiaw0PdYAI0Z6Qz2a5zA6U9IBFvwUNpjEe9tZ50Cx9DSgoTZMfmk8SEIWEyxd815kIUbs2H7dhyphenhyphenlUzfAe4yXGPB79fJiG0AXIPcw7BQKZdPyKGXlGERrx0Fn-wyoM3bdWddSftWAIqqHNH5/s1600/DSC05672.jpg\" title=\"Le gâteau nantais\" width=\"438\" /></a></div> <br /> <a name=\"more\"></a><br /> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiNneAWHjcdFU4196elFSQ15M3vRfYGclhWhomt2favHDVciS3rP1oo9J9W5lJfqiGundOr1ORF6gShkbu4TJaVGYwdncwfv5YzT6W5u20hZBlxmBZV10C1624L-0yv9XGPqFgwcsespntz/s1600/9+mars+2014.jpg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img alt=\"Le gâteau nantais\" border=\"0\" height=\"363\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiNneAWHjcdFU4196elFSQ15M3vRfYGclhWhomt2favHDVciS3rP1oo9J9W5lJfqiGundOr1ORF6gShkbu4TJaVGYwdncwfv5YzT6W5u20hZBlxmBZV10C1624L-0yv9XGPqFgwcsespntz/s1600/9+mars+2014.jpg\" title=\"Le gâteau nantais\" width=\"581\" /></a></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"></span></div> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">J</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">'vous</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"> le dis tout de suite : je suis dégoutée d'avoir découvert ce gâteau ! C'est la cata, le drame, l'horreur.&nbsp;Un conseil, partez tout de suite avant qu'il ne soit trop tard...</span><br /> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Courez.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Fuyez.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Et ne vous retournez pas.</span></div> <br /> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Pfffff....mais on n'a pas le droit d'envoyer des recettes pareilles aux gens ! Oui, parce que c'est une recette que l'une d'entre vous m'a envoyé il y a longtemps, et que je gardais précieusement. Le temps est passé et je ne me souviens plus du prénom de la personne en question - honte à moi- mais je ne la remercie pas ! Qu'est-ce qu'il m'a pris d'essayer ça ???</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">C'EST UNE TUERIE ATOMIQUE NUCLÉAIRE INTERGALACTIQUE &nbsp;!!!!&nbsp;</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Je ne m'en suis toujours pas remise...</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Alors je vous explique : le bilan calorique est juste terrifiant, mais le souvenir papillesque sera impérissable ! </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\">Eternel dilemme...</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: black; font-family: &quot;times&quot;;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Si vous adorez le beurre, le bon goût de l'amande et la saveur du rhum, vous allez fondre !</span></span></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Par contre il faut normalement 60g de rhum en tout, à savoir 20g dans la pâte, 20g pour l'arroser à la sortie du four, et 20g dans le glaçage. Je trouve que c'est absolument immangeable si on en met autant, alors je préfère mettre 15g de rhum dans la pâte, et 10g dans le glaçage, ça suffit largement.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Allez, faites taire deux minutes la petite voix qui vous rappelle que c'est bientôt la playa, planquez vos Terraillon, dégainez la poudre d'amande, débouchez le rhum, et sortez les chapeaux ronds !&nbsp;</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><b><u>RÉALISATION : Pour un moule (ou un cercle) de 20cm de diamètre :</u></b></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">3 oeufs à température ambiante bien sûr !</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">125g de beurre demi-sel très mou</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">150g de sucre en poudre </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\">(100g pour moi, et deux sachets de sucre vanillé)</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">125g de poudre d'amandes</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">40g de farine</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">15g de rhum brun</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">50g de sucre glace et 10g de rhum (pour le glaçage)</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Pas de recette en images, c'est trop facile !!!</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Préchauffez le four à </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">170&#176; chaleur tournante</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Beurrez et farinez votre moule, ou mieux, utilisez ça :</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"> <a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYri0QQlSW5AD4FscXPwK2tu0G_EcM_LVBM0UnbF5tS_6v5sZJwZG1k6oGYSGxrLgAQabi2o2B5Y-Rn4iFtyT_ZSxgksE5l8m3JGnBufh07Je0-Z7leCd6OiYxhvSl7Bx8F_DbC2o35Rx_/s1600/Unknown.jpeg\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYri0QQlSW5AD4FscXPwK2tu0G_EcM_LVBM0UnbF5tS_6v5sZJwZG1k6oGYSGxrLgAQabi2o2B5Y-Rn4iFtyT_ZSxgksE5l8m3JGnBufh07Je0-Z7leCd6OiYxhvSl7Bx8F_DbC2o35Rx_/s1600/Unknown.jpeg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"> <br /></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Je ne vous raconte pas le gain de temps...vous n'aurez plus jamais besoin de beurrer et fariner les moules, et le démoulage sera fantastique. Je ne sais pas comment j'ai pu vivre tout ce temps sans... En fait je comptais l'acheter depuis longtemps, et puis il s'est retrouvé devant moi dans un magasin, et j'ai foncé ! Le meilleur achat de ma vie...</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Dans la cuve de votre batteur fouettez longuement à vitesse max les </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">125g de beurre demi-sel très mou avec le sucre en poudre.</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"> Le mélange doit </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">bien blanchir et devenir crémeux (5 bonnes minutes au moins)</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">.</span></div> <CENTER> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5663145038303160\" data-ad-slot=\"9247665737\"></ins> </CENTER> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Ajoutez ensuite</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">&nbsp;les 3 oeufs un à un</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">, en fouettant bien à chaque fois, puis </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">les 15g de rhum</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Versez la poudre d'amande et fouettez un peu pour l'incorporer.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Ajoutez enfin les</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">40g de farine et fouettez à peine</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"> (on mélange toujours très peu à partir du moment où l'on incorpore la farine).</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Versez la pâte dans le moule, et enfournez pour </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">environ 45mn </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">(ce gâteau ne lèvera quasiment pas durant la cuisson, &nbsp;c'est normal)</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">. Il doit être vraiment bien doré !</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Démoulez-le </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">sur une grille</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"> à la sortie du four,</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"> laissez-le à l'envers</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">, et laissez bien refroidir </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\">(c'est à ce moment-là que l'on est censé l'arroser d'encore 20g de rhum, mais je n'ose même pas y penser !).</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\"><br /></span></div> <CENTER> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5663145038303160\" data-ad-slot=\"9247665737\"></ins> </CENTER> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Lorsque le gâteau est froid, mélangez les </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">5</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">0g de sucre glace et les 10g de rhum</span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">, et versez doucement ce glaçage sur le gâteau, afin d'en recouvrir uniquement le dessus (aidez-vous d'une spatule). Laissez figer et dégustez !&nbsp;</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Ce gâteau est réputé pour être </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">bien meilleur le lendemain </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\">(comme tous les gâteaux en fait...), <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: large;\">mais il est déjà magnifique le jour même !</span></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif;\"><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"font-size: large;\">Il est également connu&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">pour sa longue conservation : il paraît qu'on peut le conserver </span><span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: purple; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">jusqu'à un mois, bien emballé au frais.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Je l'ai tout de suite congelé en fines tranches pour qu'il soit hors de ma vue...</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\">Vous venez de trouver le meilleur ami de vos cups of tea.</span></div> <div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: justify;\"> <span class=\"Apple-style-span\" style=\"color: #999999; font-family: &quot;trebuchet ms&quot; , sans-serif; font-size: large;\"><br /></span></div> <br /></td></tr> </tbody></table> <br /> <ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-5663145038303160\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"5902905208\" style=\"display: block;\"></ins> </div> </div> <div class='post-footer'> <div class='post-footer-line post-footer-line-1'> <div class='byline post-share-buttons goog-inline-block'> <div aria-owns='sharing-popup-Blog1-footer-1-4089170631950631178' class='sharing' data-title='Le gâteau nantais'> <button aria-controls