d=\"c9141431068482323116-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7315068117569494880\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/08052407275223050892\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unknown</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395090404907#c7315068117569494880\">17 mars, 2014 22:06</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Wahouuu Valérie...venant de toi c est un sacré compliment...je suis plus qu intriguée!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-255223620\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7315068117569494880\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7315068117569494880-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7315068117569494880-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7315068117569494880-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7315068117569494880\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7315068117569494880-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5780893780757617765\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/05238750328938484440\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unknown</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1398206175184#c5780893780757617765\">23 avril, 2014 00:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ça ressemble au pithiviers fondant : aussi calorique mais aussi bon.<br>Je remplace le rhum du glaçage par du jus de citron, c&#39;est plus frais au goût et ça relève le goût du rhum du gateau</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1641049238\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5780893780757617765\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5780893780757617765-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5780893780757617765-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5780893780757617765-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5780893780757617765\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5780893780757617765-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6903326569316644312-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6903326569316644312\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6903326569316644312-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3286939073483495099\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Laure</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1394994962918#c3286939073483495099\">16 mars, 2014 19:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mon beau-père vient d&#39;apprendre à faire le gâteau nantais chez Ducasse, et nous l&#39;a servir avec des bananes au caramel pour l&#39;anniversaire de ma père. de fait, c&#39;est un régal. Lui avait respecté la dose de rhum, et je dois dire que je le trouvais bien imbibé... Je pense que quand je m&#39;y mettrais, je vais suivre ton conseil de réduire la quantité !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3286939073483495099\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3286939073483495099\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3286939073483495099-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3286939073483495099-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4163196442815176097\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1394997026386#c4163196442815176097\">16 mars, 2014 20:10</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Avec des bananes au caramel !!!! Ca devait être féérique, mais ensuite on ne mange plus pendant 3 semaines... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4163196442815176097\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4163196442815176097-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4163196442815176097-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4163196442815176097-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4163196442815176097\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4163196442815176097-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4459715699611213314\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Laure</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1394999312819#c4459715699611213314\">16 mars, 2014 20:48</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Voilà. Ou alors, on fait des madeleines, des asperges sauce hollandaise... - et on met toute sa mauvaise foi à nier le fait que les maillots de bain, ça va venir vite. ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4459715699611213314\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4459715699611213314-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><s