ml?showComment=1395060601065#c2738371584844312448\">17 mars, 2014 13:50</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Et oui c&#39;est bien moi ! Je reconnaitrais ma recette entre mille meme privee de mes papilles..... Sans rancune j&#39;espere ?!... ;-) </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2738371584844312448\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2738371584844312448-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2738371584844312448-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2738371584844312448-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2738371584844312448\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2738371584844312448-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c926553838774963263\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/15098110237523438392\" rel=\"nofollow\">44fabienx</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1398382305963#c926553838774963263\">25 avril, 2014 01:31</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">&quot;Ta&quot; recette existe depuis le début des années 1800, tu peux m&#39;expliquer ta recette de longévité?</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1478565734\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/926553838774963263\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c926553838774963263-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c926553838774963263-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c926553838774963263-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"926553838774963263\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c926553838774963263-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6052251066003691980-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6052251066003691980\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6052251066003691980-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c873092555105309219\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Laura</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395003626328#c873092555105309219\">16 mars, 2014 22:00</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je viens de relire la recette.... Il faut imperativement arroser du 2eme tiers de rhum apres le demoulage !!!! C&#39;est encore mieux ne crains rien !!! (De toute facon au point ou on en est dans la tuerie culinaire a ce stade plus rien n&#39;est grave...) Fais moi confiance et fonce sur le prochain.... </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"873092555105309219\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/873092555105309219\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c873092555105309219-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c873092555105309219-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1157744236646040463\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395047003464#c1157744236646040463\">17 mars, 2014 10:03</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">J&#39;ai peur... ;))</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1157744236646040463\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1157744236646040463-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1157744236646040463-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1157744236646040463-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1157744236646040463\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1157744236646040463-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3394274524594096894\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Laura</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395060170484#c3394274524594096894\">17 mars, 2014 13:42</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Lance-toi sur l&#39;arrosage sortie de four fais-moi confiance... </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3394274524594096894\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3394274524594096894-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3394274524594096894-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3394274524594096894-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3394274524594096894\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3394274524594096894-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c873092555105309219-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"873092555105309219\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c873092555105309219-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3325649160727982587\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"http://enviedebiscuiter.blogspot.fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Graine de Vanille</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395004397518#c3325649160727982587\">16 mars, 2014 22:13</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Hum&#8230; très tentant en effet&#8230; beurre, poudre d&#39;amandes, rhum : le trio gagnant quoi !!! ;-)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3325649160727982587\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3325649160727982587\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3325649160727982587-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3325649160727982587-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7853659634504501300\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395047101637#c7853659634504501300\">17 mars, 2014 10:05</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je crois qu&#39;on n&#39;a rien créé de mieux... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7853659634504501300\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7853659634504501300-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7853659634504501300-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7853659634504501300-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7853659634504501300\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7853659634504501300-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c3325649160727982587-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3325649160727982587\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3325649160727982587-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1553489065276602993\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Mirna</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395005384206#c1553489065276602993\">16 mars, 2014 22:29</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ça je confirme, niveau calorie c&#39;est pire que tout ! On les sent à chaque bouchée que l&#39;on prend. Mais c&#39;est tellement bon. J&#39;ai réalisé ce gâteau à la suite du &quot;Meilleur pâtissier&quot; car c&#39;était une de leur épreuve et j&#39;ai de suite était séduite surtout quand j&#39;ai vu cette jolie mie jaunâtre transparente et dense qui nous dévoile la présence et le bon goût de l&#39;amande et du beurre. <br>Vu qu&#39;il doit bien falloir au minimum 352 jours pour éliminer les calories et la cellulite que ce gâteau engendre, je vais te faire faux bon parce que moi j&#39;y ai déjà eu plus que droit (si tu vois ce que je veux dire). En plus je suis sûre que comme toujours ta recette est bien meilleure que toutes les autres et je ne serais pas me limiter à une part.<br>Moi qui voulait te parler d&#39;une recette à tester, je vais te laisser te remettre durant quelques mois je pense ;-)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1553489065276602993\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1553489065276602993\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1553489065276602993-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1553489065276602993-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7722285258831762786\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067402142#c7722285258831762786\">17 mars, 2014 15:43</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ah mais je ne me souviens pas du tout l&#39;avoir vu dans cette émission ! C&#39;est fou ça, je ne l&#39;ai jamais ratée ! <br>Tu as raison, ne le fais pas, ça vaut mieux... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7722285258831762786\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7722285258831762786-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7722285258831762786-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7722285258831762786-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7722285258831762786\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7722285258831762786-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3596794165234330375\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Mirna</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395131255109#c3596794165234330375\">18 mars, 2014 09:27</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Autant pour moi ! j&#39;ai à peine lu ta recette j&#39;ai vu amande, rhum, beurre et j&#39;ai pensé au gâteau voyageur qui a pourtant beaucoup moins de beurre. Mais il m&#39;avait paru hyper calorique alors qu&#39;est ce que ça va être avec celui là. <br><br>Bon ben du coup je n&#39;ai pas le choix je dois passer moi aussi par la case &quot;test&quot; et faire ce gâteau. Je l&#8217;emmènerai aux collègues, en plus il y en a une qui est au régime ça va lui faire plaisir ;-)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3596794165234330375\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3596794165234330375-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3596794165234330375-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3596794165234330375-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3596794165234330375\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3596794165234330375-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4936138236121146425\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395145924299#c4936138236121146425\">18 mars, 2014 13:32</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">La pauvre...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4936138236121146425\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4936138236121146425-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4936138236121146425-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4936138236121146425-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4936138236121146425\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4936138236121146425-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c1553489065276602993-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1553489065276602993\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1553489065276602993-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3576434037053324626\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiLXHqdLy10NPTMHxtAq2GAijPXDZcxVJUU0SjeLUxb9Ue-TO-fmqUmy_fAsMskE33-OdCht4eeVB0D_i5CBmiR5abuY4dPaFGNXNi_-Mq17hlLEndGMzYAXO-4TKHgTw/s45-c/avatarmylittlepatisserie_langue.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/18334901949747016186\" rel=\"nofollow\">mylittlepatisserie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395013630911#c3576434037053324626\">17 mars, 2014 00:47</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Il m&#39;a l&#39;air d&#39;être bien gourmand ce gâteau, en tout cas , je ne suis pas encore parti, je reste ;)<br><br>(chouette glaçage au passage)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3576434037053324626\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-740234674\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3576434037053324626\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3576434037053324626-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3576434037053324626-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3576434037053324626-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3576434037053324626\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3576434037053324626-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8534122526622580017\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395034027599#c8534122526622580017\">17 mars, 2014 06:27</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je me réjouis de le faire samedi pour les 80 ans de ma mère et je peux imaginer que ses amies ne se feront aucun souci pour les calories............. Miam....<br>As-tu déjà congelé des jaunes d&#8217;œufs et si oui comment ? Marie-Claire</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8534122526622580017\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8534122526622580017\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8534122526622580017-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8534122526622580017-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2380688778608144711\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067333672#c2380688778608144711\">17 mars, 2014 15:42</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Vivement qu&#39;on ait 80 ans... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2380688778608144711\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2380688778608144711-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2380688778608144711-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2380688778608144711-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2380688778608144711\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2380688778608144711-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c8534122526622580017-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8534122526622580017\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8534122526622580017-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8948963181700302797\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Julien Lartiste</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395041348951#c8948963181700302797\">17 mars, 2014 08:29</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Valérie, petite question bête pour un nouvel utilisateur de KitchenAid : pour crémer le beurre avec le sucre, ça se fait avec le fouet ou avec la feuille ? D&#39;après les instructions le fouet est fait pour monter les blancs en neige et les préparations &quot;liquides&quot;, donc je me pose la question. <br><br>Merci :)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8948963181700302797\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8948963181700302797\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8948963181700302797-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8948963181700302797-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5318818811572154535\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395046978897#c5318818811572154535\">17 mars, 2014 10:02</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">En fait on crème normalement le sucre et le beurre à la feuille, mais je préfère vraiment le faire au fouet. Je trouve que ça marche mieux. Par contre il faut que le beurre soit très mou !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5318818811572154535\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5318818811572154535-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5318818811572154535-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5318818811572154535-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5318818811572154535\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5318818811572154535-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c8948963181700302797-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8948963181700302797\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8948963181700302797-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9171285229707247440\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Audrey poussinne74</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395044962959#c9171285229707247440\">17 mars, 2014 09:29</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ouh la la je salive d&#39;avance !!!! Par contre ma mère qui vient de recevoir ces résultats pour le cholestérol va être dégoutée !!! Après le boulot ... ma mission aller chercher du beurre demi-sel !!! Merci pour toutes tes recettes et toutes tes astuces!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9171285229707247440\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9171285229707247440\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9171285229707247440-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9171285229707247440-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c9171285229707247440-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9171285229707247440\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9171285229707247440-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9065180709748457569\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Sissie</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395046219666#c9065180709748457569\">17 mars, 2014 09:50</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">ma grand-mère nous en faisait plusieurs fois par semaine pendant les vacances, c&#39;est un régal! J&#39;avais juste le souvenir de ce gâteau aux amandes et &quot;à l&#39;alcool&quot; (pour les enfants que nous étions, c&#39;était juste de l&#39;alcool) délicieux, mais je ne connaissais ni le nom ni la recette. je suis ravie de le retrouver, ce sera un bon souvenir des vacances en famille. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9065180709748457569\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9065180709748457569\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9065180709748457569-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9065180709748457569-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c9065180709748457569-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9065180709748457569\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9065180709748457569-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2931770406573289371\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/14447393187769424093\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frankounette</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395046584673#c2931770406573289371\">17 mars, 2014 09:56</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Avec une intro comme ça et ces quelques photos, on ne pouvait que cliquer pour voir la suite :) Il me tente beaucoup ce gâteau! C&#39;est décidé malgré les appels du bikini je le teste vendredi! Une simple question, c&#39;est important d&#39;utiliser du rhum brun? le rhum blanc pourrait convenir? </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2931770406573289371\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1285056947\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2931770406573289371\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2931770406573289371-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2931770406573289371-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8636447824999616980\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395046901977#c8636447824999616980\">17 mars, 2014 10:01</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Il se fait normalement avec du brun, mais ça marche aussi très bien avec le blanc. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8636447824999616980\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8636447824999616980-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8636447824999616980-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8636447824999616980-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8636447824999616980\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8636447824999616980-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1571926608044603592\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/14447393187769424093\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frankounette</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395343408971#c1571926608044603592\">20 mars, 2014 20:23</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Il est en train de tranquillement attendre que nous le dégustions demain soir ;) Je vais donc le mettre au frigo comme tu le suggères. <br>Pour info, j&#39;ai utilisé du rhum blanc vu que c&#39;est tout ce que j&#39;avais dans mon bar :) </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1285056947\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1571926608044603592\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1571926608044603592-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1571926608044603592-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1571926608044603592-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1571926608044603592\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1571926608044603592-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c2931770406573289371-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2931770406573289371\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2931770406573289371-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c409600944932564903\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"http://cookingwithclementine.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Clémentine</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395050420568#c409600944932564903\">17 mars, 2014 11:00</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie!<br>Votre blog est une petite merveille. Vos recettes ont toujours un énorme succès chez moi.<br>Aujourd&#39;hui, je me décide à vous écrire. Vos photos mais surtout vous recettes sont exquises<br>Votre gâteau nantais a l&#39;air délicieux. Je suis Nantaise et je n&#39;avais jamais encore trouvé une recette qui me tentait mais bien entendu, vous me l&#39;apportez sur un plateau d&#39;argent.<br>Dès que je le fais, je vous envoie un petit commentaire.<br>Et encore bravo et merci pour toutes vos recette :-)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"409600944932564903\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/409600944932564903\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c409600944932564903-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c409600944932564903-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2794051922751908684\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067299383#c2794051922751908684\">17 mars, 2014 15:41</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Vous êtes nantaise ??? Alors vous êtes obligée de le faire ! </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2794051922751908684\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2794051922751908684-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2794051922751908684-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2794051922751908684-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2794051922751908684\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2794051922751908684-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c409600944932564903-continue\"