rs, 2014 13:32</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Sinon tu peux toujours le manger en pédalant dans l&#39;eau...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3413203313100204906\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3413203313100204906-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3413203313100204906-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3413203313100204906-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3413203313100204906\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3413203313100204906-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7832235535661268173\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395164413558#c7832235535661268173\">18 mars, 2014 18:40</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">why not ? et à la place de la bouteille d&#39;eau sur le bord de la piscine je prévois un ti-punch ......autant ça me fait pédaler plus vite et plus longtemps....</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7832235535661268173\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7832235535661268173-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7832235535661268173-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7832235535661268173-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7832235535661268173\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7832235535661268173-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c2208194023493695686-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2208194023493695686\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2208194023493695686-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c904027180531491427\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Cécile</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395051533511#c904027180531491427\">17 mars, 2014 11:18</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie,<br>Je tiens à vous féliciter pour votre blog que je visite chaque semaine depuis plus d&#39;un an.<br>Vos recettes sont parfaites. Le nutella a quitté nos placards depuis la michalaka! <br>Concernant le gâteau nantais, j&#39;ai testé la recette il y a quelques mois (avec les 60g de rhum!) et ça a été une vrai révélation. Je crois que c&#39;est devenu notre gâteau préféré (il y a aussi le cake marocain de Sophie Dudemaine qui se défend bien). Souvent, je me dis que les gâteaux les plus simples sont les meilleurs. Pour preuve également le marbré dont vous avez publié la recette il y a peu de temps.<br>Continuez de nous régaler, c&#39;est super</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"904027180531491427\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/904027180531491427\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c904027180531491427-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c904027180531491427-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5844664127148665464\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067203847#c5844664127148665464\">17 mars, 2014 15:40</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Tout à fait d&#39;accord : ce sont les choses les plus simples les meilleures !!! Ce gateau nantais en est la preuve... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5844664127148665464\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5844664127148665464-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5844664127148665464-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5844664127148665464-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5844664127148665464\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5844664127148665464-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6905991597516885356\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395808074449#c6905991597516885356\">26 mars, 2014 05:27</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour,<br>Merci de partager avec nous vos sublimes recettes.<br>Super le blog, super...... les recettes, super.....les explications et super.... la façon dont vous nous donnez l&#39;envie d&#39;essayer. Encore merci.<br>Au fait, c&#39;est quoi la &quot;michalaka&quot; ? les recettes de C. Michalak ou quelque chose de spécial ?<br><br>Corcialement<br><br>Odette (Désolée, je n&#39;ai pas de blog)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6905991597516885356\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6905991597516885356-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6905991597516885356-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6905991597516885356-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6905991597516885356\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6905991597516885356-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1138360128694454295\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395835225279#c1138360128694454295\">26 mars, 2014 13:00</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">C&#39;est tout simplement la pâte à tartiner de Michalak, que j&#39;ai baptisée &quot;Michakella&quot;. <br>Voici la recette : <br>http://www.cestmafournee.com/2013/04/avant-il-y-avait-le-nutellamais-ca.html</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1138360128694454295\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1138360128694454295-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1138360128694454295-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1138360128694454295-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1138360128694454295\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1138360128694454295-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c904027180531491427-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"904027180531491427\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c904027180531491427-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8033151207103005850\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">marion</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395051757648#c8033151207103005850\">17 mars, 2014 11:22</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Moi je le fais avec 75gr de beurre et 150g d&#39;amandes et pas de farine! :p</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8033151207103005850\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8033151207103005850\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8033151207103005850-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8033151207103005850-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5496347498128978885\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067098876#c5496347498128978885\">17 mars, 2014 15:38</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Oui j&#39;ai vu qu&#39;il existait des versions sans farine, effectivement.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5496347498128978885\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5496347498128978885-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5496347498128978885-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5496347498128978885-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5496347498128978885\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5496347498128978885-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c8033151207103005850-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8033151207103005850\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8033151207103005850-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6920193409539510404\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/16073252118866817099\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nadine</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395053935433#c6920193409539510404\">17 mars, 2014 11:58</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Cette recette me tente beaucoup mais...eh oui, il y a un &quot;mais&quot;...elle est au beurre. Serait-il possible de mettre de mettre de la margarine &quot;goût beurre&quot; et une petite cuillère à café de sel ?</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6920193409539510404\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-141532943\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6920193409539510404\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6920193409539510404-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6920193409539510404-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3586188767529193020\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067077471#c3586188767529193020\">17 mars, 2014 15:37</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Oui c&#39;est tout à fait possible, si on n&#39;a pas le choix... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3586188767529193020\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3586188767529193020-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3586188767529193020-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3586188767529193020-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3586188767529193020\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3586188767529193020-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6920193409539510404-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6920193409539510404\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6920193409539510404-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3760136936638289102\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395056327104#c3760136936638289102\">17 mars, 2014 12:38</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">waouw ce gateau m a l air delicieux ,<br>pourrait on remplacer le rhum par autre chose non alcolise .<br>merci pour toutes vos recettes ainsi que vos photos fabuleuses.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3760136936638289102\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3760136936638289102\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3760136936638289102-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3760136936638289102-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4773202563449388249\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067269815#c4773202563449388249\">17 mars, 2014 15:41</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je ne sais pas du tout. Je pense que le mieux serait tout simplement de mettre les graines d&#39;une belle gousse de vanille avec le beurre et le sucre dès le départ, et de faire le glaçage avec de l&#39;eau.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4773202563449388249\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4773202563449388249-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4773202563449388249-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4773202563449388249-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4773202563449388249\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4773202563449388249-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c3760136936638289102-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3760136936638289102\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3760136936638289102-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2492747490596471139\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03277576537730698748\" rel=\"nofollow\">Madry</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395056673420#c2492747490596471139\">17 mars, 2014 12:44</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Rahhhh vade retro calorico !!!!!!<br>Ce gâteau me fait diaboliquement envie, mais voilà, j&#39;ai décidé de reprendre le régime alors éventuellement en &quot;joker&quot; quitte à en prendre un, autant se faire plaisir. Rien que les photos sentent le beurre et les amandes ! Mon problème va être le rhum, on n&#39;a pas d&#39;alcool à la maison, faudrait que je fasse un sirop bien parfumé pour remplacer, mais ça n&#39;aura évidemment pas le même goût.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2492747490596471139\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-278760443\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2492747490596471139\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2492747490596471139-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2492747490596471139-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2760336742686047652\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395067028233#c2760336742686047652\">17 mars, 2014 15:37</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Sans sucre le sirop alors ! <br>Je pense que le mieux est de mettre les graines d&#39;une belle gousse de vanille avec le beurre et le sucre dès le départ, et de se passer de rhum, tant pis...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2760336742686047652\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2760336742686047652-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2760336742686047652-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2760336742686047652-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2760336742686047652\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2760336742686047652-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c2492747490596471139-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2492747490596471139\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2492747490596471139-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8118516928379867671\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">évelyne</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395060284157#c8118516928379867671\">17 mars, 2014 13:44</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">bonjour, je confirme ce gâteau est une bombe!! Son vrai nom est &quot;Gâteau LU&quot; du nom de son créateur (la biscuiterie LU) il y a très longtemps. Je le fais régulièrement :(.L&#39;indispensable est de le cuire dans un moule aluminium jetable (diam 22 cm), de ne pas le faire trop cuire (le centre doit être juste cuit) et surtout NE PAS LE DEMOULER. L&#39;arroser dès la sortie du four avec le rhum BRUN. Il faut vraiment 10 cl rhum (en tout) : le gâteau doit être assez humide et il ne sera pas plus fort (si,si!!) mais tellement plus moelleux . Merci pour votre réponse à ma question sur la congélation des pains hamburger : ils sont top!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8118516928379867671\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8118516928379867671\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8118516928379867671-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8118516928379867671-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3419206018379509612\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395066945978#c3419206018379509612\">17 mars, 2014 15:35</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Evelyne, voici l&#39;histoire du gâteau nantais :<br>&quot;Le gâteau nantais est probablement né au XVIIIe siècle, alors que les quais de la Fosse ou de l&#8217;île Feydeau accueillaient les trésors en provenance des Antilles : sucre de canne, rhum ambré, vanille bourbon&#8230; Le chroniqueur Paul Eudel en attribue la paternité à un certain Rouleau, maître fouacier, installé en 1820 rue Saint-Clément. Ce dessert haut de gamme, que faisaient servir les maîtresses de maison à leurs invités quand elles tenaient salon, avait fini par sombrer quelque<br> peu dans l&#8217;oubli jusqu&#8217;à sa relance par la biscuiterie LU, de 1910 à 1972. Depuis, les pâtissiers et les cuisiniers de la ville de Nantes en proposent des adaptations artisanales&quot;.<br>Lu ne l&#39;a donc pas créé ;)<br>Le fait de le démouler permet d&#39;obtenir une surface très lisse, qui pourra recevoir joliment le glaçage. <br>J&#39;ai très peur de l&#39;arroser de rhum à la sortie du four...mais je le ferai par curiosité la prochaine fois. ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3419206018379509612\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3419206018379509612-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3419206018379509612-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3419206018379509612-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3419206018379509612\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3419206018379509612-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4669321714435481833\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">évelyne</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395077410535#c4669321714435481833\">17 mars, 2014 18:30</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">oui, je n&#39;aurais pas dû employer le mot créateur mais plutôt &quot;relanceur&quot;:( , je ne voulais pas vous froisser. Je suis Nantaise, et c&#39;est vrai qu&#39;il est difficile d&#39;en trouver de très bons. Oui, le démoulage donne un glaçage lisse mais normalement le dessus du gâteau est assez lisse et le moule alu jetable apporte tellement un plus (sûrement parce qu&#39;il refroidit dans le moule) mais pour la présentation c&#39;est plus discutable. Du coup, j&#39;en ai encore fait un cet après-midi, aïe, aïe, aïe!!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4669321714435481833\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4669321714435481833-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4669321714435481833-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4669321714435481833-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4669321714435481833\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4669321714435481833-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6611792953403339591\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395146187315#c6611792953403339591\">18 mars, 2014 13:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mais je ne suis pas du tout froissée ! Je suis désolée d&#39;avoir donnée cette impression.<br> </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6611792953403339591\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6611792953403339591-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6611792953403339591-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6611792953403339591-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6611792953403339591\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6611792953403339591-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c8118516928379867671-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8118516928379867671\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8118516928379867671-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9189123636563561057\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395063394738#c9189123636563561057\">17 mars, 2014 14:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour valerie,<br><br>Pour une version sanq alcool - par quoi pourrai-je remplacer le rhum stp ?<br><br>Un grand merci<br>Tamy</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9189123636563561057\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9189123636563561057\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9189123636563561057-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9189123636563561057-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2601045576344444690\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395066734865#c2601045576344444690\">17 mars, 2014 15:32</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je ne sais pas du tout. Je pense que le mieux serait tout simplement de mettre les graines d&#39;une belle gousse de vanille avec le beurre et le sucre dès le départ, et de faire le glaçage avec de l&#39;eau.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2601045576344444690\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2601045576344444690-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2601045576344444690-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2601045576344444690-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2601045576344444690\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2601045576344444690-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2644670201689765402\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Naïma</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395077543998#c2644670201689765402\">17 mars, 2014 18:32</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ne consommant pas d&#39;alcool, pour toutes les recettes utilisant du rhum, j&#39;utilise le sirop MONIN saveur Rhum Caribbean. C&#39;est un bon substitut.<br>Par contre vu que cette recette est déjà très sucré, je me demande si c&#39;est l&#39;idéal. Je vais tester comme ça quand même. Le glaçage est-il indispensable ?</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2644670201689765402\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2644670201689765402-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2644670201689765402-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2644670201689765402-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2644670201689765402\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2644670201689765402-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9107207096940281345\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03277576537730698748\" rel=\"nofollow\">Madry</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395142313916#c9107207096940281345\">18 mars, 2014 12:31</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Pas d&#39;alcool chez nous non plus ... mais en y repensant, on trouve de l&#8217;arôme &quot;Rhum&quot;, à diluer dans un sirop léger pour éviter de rajouter du sucre. Sinon reste la vanille ou un sirop (léger encore) à l&#39;orange ou au citron. Voire de l&#8217;arôme amande amère, même si je ne suis pas spécialement fan à titre personnel.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-278760443\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9107207096940281345\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9107207096940281345-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9107207096940281345-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c9107207096940281345-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9107207096940281345\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9107207096940281345-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3314787015528266097\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395146461154#c3314787015528266097\">18 mars, 2014 13:41</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Oui, vous pouvez utiliser de l&#39;arôme rhum concentré, que vous ajouterez à la pâte. <br>Le glaçage permet une bonne conservation du gâteau, mais n&#39;est pas indispensable. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3314787015528266097\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3314787015528266097-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3314787015528266097-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3314787015528266097-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3314787015528266097\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3314787015528266097-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c9189123636563561057-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9189123636563561057\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9189123636563561057-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6533348101450815995\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Typhaine</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395066250260#c6533348101450815995\">17 mars, 2014 15:24</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ça à l&#39;air tellement bon !!!<br>PS : je trouve que vous pourriez participer à la prochaine émission du &quot;meilleur pâtissier&quot; !!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6533348101450815995\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6533348101450815995\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6533348101450815995-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6533348101450815995-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6533348101450815995-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6533348101450815995\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6533348101450815995-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3335063153398446247\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Pink</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395073654428#c3335063153398446247\">17 mars, 2014 17:27</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ahalala encore une recette délicieuse à tester! Le cake au citron est déjà devenu un must de mon carnet de recette! Cependant je m&#39;interroge sur l&#39;utilisation du spray aérosol de chez ancel, ça a l&#39;air pratique mais quand je vois les ingrédients c&#39;est &quot;huile végétale&quot; donc huile de palme ce n&#39;est pas terrible non? Et niveau écologique de même, enfin, chacun fait comme il l&#39;entend j&#39;imagine mais ça m&#39;étonne de vous voir l&#39;utiliser vu la qualité des ingrédients que vous utilisez par ailleurs! Sinon un grand merci pour toutes ces recettes et bonne continuation!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3335063153398446247\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3335063153398446247\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3335063153398446247-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3335063153398446247-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5427841959816347092\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395146300292#c5427841959816347092\">18 mars, 2014 13:38</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mais la quantité est infime !!!! Il s&#39;agit juste de tapisser un moule, pas de faire une pâte à tartiner avec... ;))<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5427841959816347092\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5427841959816347092-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5427841959816347092-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5427841959816347092-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5427841959816347092\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5427841959816347092-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c3335063153398446247-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3335063153398446247\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3335063153398446247-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7770594854093446418\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Isabelle H</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395075033233#c7770594854093446418\">17 mars, 2014 17:50</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je me demande si ce n est pas le meme que le gateau appelé Le Voyageur dans l emission Le Meilleur Patissier, ca vous dit quelque chose? Ils avaient dit que c etait une tres vieille recette. C est la premiere fois que je contribue sur votre blog, Valerie, et il faut que je vous dise que j ai passe tout l apres midi de samedi a decouvrir vos recettes et je ne sais pas combien de temps je vais résister! J aime bcp votre sens de l humour de coups de gueule! ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7770594854093446418\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7770594854093446418\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7770594854093446418-rt\" clas