ssible ça! Je mets direct en favoris (mais il n&#39;y restera pas longtemps, il sera testé très vite!).</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8987392076509201696\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8987392076509201696\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8987392076509201696-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8987392076509201696-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8987392076509201696-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8987392076509201696\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8987392076509201696-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6792702923411154244\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11386926102852350676\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blandine</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395131614924#c6792702923411154244\">18 mars, 2014 09:33</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mon mari m&#39;a juste dit un rictus aux lèvres...&quot;ah oui c&#39;est bien le gâteau de ma maman&quot;...Nous sommes tous les 2 nantais expatriés et personnellement je ne connaissais pas ce gâteau...Je l&#39;ai fait hier soir...et ce gout d&#39;amande c&#39;est trop addictif!!!! Apparemment la version que connaissait mon cher et tendre était elle aussi bcp plus imbibée de rhum!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6792702923411154244\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1951676009\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6792702923411154244\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6792702923411154244-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6792702923411154244-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5098377036236823941\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395144285300#c5098377036236823941\">18 mars, 2014 13:04</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Blandine tu es trop forte ! A chaque fois tu testes tout très vite, et tu reviens toujours me donner ton avis. Merci beaucoup.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5098377036236823941\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5098377036236823941-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle t