/p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8456561867538962578\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8456561867538962578-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8456561867538962578-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8456561867538962578-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8456561867538962578\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8456561867538962578-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3649313962679692291\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Béatrice</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395211191562#c3649313962679692291\">19 mars, 2014 07:39</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je l&#39;ai refait avec tes doses.<br>il est top.<br>Et mon mari a préféré lui aussi ta version!<br>Merci encore pour ta recette. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3649313962679692291\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3649313962679692291-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"threa