omment-content\">Ah ah ah !!! </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7653298539459970830\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7653298539459970830-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7653298539459970830-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7653298539459970830-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7653298539459970830\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7653298539459970830-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c3991167484928846071-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3991167484928846071\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3991167484928846071-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3011321059438561954\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Carolaix</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395159387501#c3011321059438561954\">18 mars, 2014 17:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour les pâtinautes!<br>Juste une information (Valérie, j&#39;espère que cela ne te dérange pas!) : le chocolat Valrhona est sur Vente Privée à partir de demain! ... miam</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3011321059438561954\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3011321059438561954\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3011321059438561954-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3011321059438561954-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8323015225823985040\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395160485461#c8323015225823985040\">18 mars, 2014 17:34</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">MERCI !!!!!!!!!!!!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8323015225823985040\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8323015225823985040-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8323015225823985040-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8323015225823985040-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8323015225823985040\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8323015225823985040-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2211102980549776305\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395165160023#c2211102980549776305\">18 mars, 2014 18:52</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Merci Carolaix.................persuadée qu&#39;il n&#39;y aurait pas de nouvelle vente après le ONEDAY de février j&#39;ai demandé à ma cousine de m&#39;en acheter car elle le trouve à 25 euros le kilos en magasin à Aubenas ( l&#39;entreprise Valrhona est en Ardéche ) .<br> </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2211102980549776305\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2211102980549776305-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2211102980549776305-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2211102980549776305-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2211102980549776305\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2211102980549776305-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8409791291075470877\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395165597965#c8409791291075470877\">18 mars, 2014 18:59</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Sinon pour les Pâtinautes parisiennes , le chocolat Valhrona est vendu chez GDETOU à des prix super intéressants ; par ex le paquet de 3 kilos Caraibes 66% est à 50 euros , en plus ils ont plus de choix que sur le site de vente privée, il y a d&#39;autres &quot;variétés&quot; en pistoles ou tablette......dommage qu&#39;ils ne vendent pas en ligne ...<br>Comme je rentrais chez moi par avion , je n&#39;ai pas pu en acheter , j&#39;avais plus de place dans mes valises..................</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8409791291075470877\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8409791291075470877-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8409791291075470877-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8409791291075470877-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8409791291075470877\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8409791291075470877-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1695122203634399089\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03277576537730698748\" rel=\"nofollow\">Madry</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395170466307#c1695122203634399089\">18 mars, 2014 20:21</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Lol grillée ! heureusement que j&#39;ai lu les comm avant d&#39;avertir !<br>Manifestement, ils en font souvent, j&#39;ai vu passer une vente en septembre, j&#39;ai commandé en décembre et là ... pour Paques :p<br>En décembre, le chocolat était à 18&#8364;/kg, forfait frais de port à 6&#8364;, il n&#39;y avait malheureusement pas toutes les références : pas de sacs par 3kg et pas forcement les meilleurs crus, mais on trouvait la couverture lait, blanche et deux variétés de noir.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-278760443\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1695122203634399089\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1695122203634399089-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1695122203634399089-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1695122203634399089-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1695122203634399089\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1695122203634399089-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4546993760279097526\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395177366139#c4546993760279097526\">18 mars, 2014 22:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ah voilà le terme &quot; cru &quot; est plus approprié que &quot; variété&quot; ! mais tout à l heure rien de mieux ne voulait sortir de ma tête ! ça doit être déjà le taux de cholestérol qui est en train de dépasser les limites autorisées et qui bouchent déjà mes artères :(((<br><br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4546993760279097526\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4546993760279097526-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4546993760279097526-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4546993760279097526-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4546993760279097526\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4546993760279097526-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3795875035548647886\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Athénaïs</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395220666145#c3795875035548647886\">19 mars, 2014 10:17</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je ne me reconnais plus... Est-ce vraiment moi qui vient de dépenser plus de 100 euros de chocolat à 7h du matin ??!? Valérie, tu m&#39;as transformée !!! (pour la bonne cause !!)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3795875035548647886\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3795875035548647886-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3795875035548647886-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3795875035548647886-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3795875035548647886\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3795875035548647886-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1052825795382304697\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395221444140#c1052825795382304697\">19 mars, 2014 10:30</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Au moins je fais marcher l&#39;économie du pays... ;))</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1052825795382304697\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1052825795382304697-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1052825795382304697-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1052825795382304697-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1052825795382304697\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1052825795382304697-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5758030603929547651\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395231549571#c5758030603929547651\">19 mars, 2014 13:19</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Coucou Valérie, <br>C&#39;est la première fois que je vais acheter du chocolat Valrhona mais je suis un peu perdue. Quel chocolat me conseilles-tu ou plutôt (je reformule) lequel vas-tu utiliser dans tes prochaines recettes ?? Maintenant, je fais ma liste de course en fonction de toi... Pour les cookies : les cuillères américaines c&#39;est ok et le frigo déborde de margarine. Pour les crêpes : après le rhum, j&#39;ai enchainé avec le Grand Marnier... Merci d&#39;avance pour tes conseils</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5758030603929547651\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5758030603929547651-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5758030603929547651-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5758030603929547651-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5758030603929547651\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5758030603929547651-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c785313827490592045\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395233896611#c785313827490592045\">19 mars, 2014 13:58</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Delphine , c&#39;est une autre Delphine et je me permets de répondre au cas où Valérie ne voit pas de suite ton message ( car les stocks sur vente privée peuvent s&#39;épuiser)<br>Perso je pense que si tu achètes du CARAIBES 66% ,et du JIVARA en pistoles c&#39;est déjà pas mal et si tu rajoutes du GUANAJA 70% c&#39;est parfait !<br>Sinon avoir dans son placard de l&#39;IVOIRE ( blanc ) c&#39;est top aussi car il est vraiment de super qualité pour l&#39;utiliser en pâtisserie mais j&#39;avoue que 1kg en pistoles ça peut faire beaucoup ( on utlise moins le chocolat blanc en général )<br>mais tu peux l&#39;acheter en tablette , il y a un lot de 2 tablettes de 250g IVOIRE à 12&#8364;, c&#39;est un peu plus cher que le kg de pistoles<br>En même temps la DLUO va &quot;en gros&quot; jusqu&#39;à 02/2015 donc ça nous laisse du temps pour l&#39;utiliser .......<br>Voilà ça c&#39;était mon avis de Pâtinaute addict au blog et à la pâtisserie <br>Par contre BIEN SUR je ne sais pas ce que Valérie nous réserve comme recettes prochainement ! mais avec toutes les sublimes recettes de son blog tu trouveras largement de quoi utiliser le chocolat ......... <br>Voilà j&#39;espère que je t&#39;aurai un peu aidée<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/785313827490592045\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c785313827490592045-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c785313827490592045-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c785313827490592045-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"785313827490592045\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c785313827490592045-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5988535436481423040\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395234857745#c5988535436481423040\">19 mars, 2014 14:14</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Salut les Delphine ! <br>Alors je ne sais pas du tout ce que seront les prochaines recettes, je vis au jour le jour... ;)<br>Pour Valrhona il faut du Caraïbes 66%, du Jivara (c&#39;est celui au lait), du cacao en poudre et des perles craquantes au chocolat (pour les mousses au choco, les cookies, le tiramisu, les entremets, la déco etc...). <br>Si tu peux ajoute du 70% le Guanaja, mais surtout surtout LA COUVERTURE IVOIRE !!! Impossible de vivre sans, notamment pour réaliser les macarons, mais surtout la superbe tarte fraises pistache de Michalak !! On ne peut pas remplacer la couverture ivoire par quoi que ce soit d&#39;autre, alors il en faut.<br>On peut aussi ajouter le caramelia pour en mettre dans les cookies !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5988535436481423040\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5988535436481423040-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5988535436481423040-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5988535436481423040-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5988535436481423040\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5988535436481423040-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1331422879140565562\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395259161883#c1331422879140565562\">19 mars, 2014 20:59</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Merci à toutes les 2 pour vos conseils. Ça y est la commande est faite : 1 Kg de Caraïbes, 1 kg de Jivara, 500g d&#39;Ivoire (pour la tarte aux fraises pistache) et 2 petites tablettes de Caramélia (juste par gourmandise). Heureusement que je me suis arrêtée là, parce que quand j&#39;ai annoncé le prix à mon chéri, il m&#39;a dit texto : &quot;On mange bien avec c&#39;est ma fournée mais elle nous revient cher !!&quot; A ce rythme là, il va me bloquer la connexion internet !!! Bizz</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1331422879140565562\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1331422879140565562-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1331422879140565562-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1331422879140565562-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1331422879140565562\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1331422879140565562-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3152302407900677436\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395262526624#c3152302407900677436\">19 mars, 2014 21:55</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Parfaite ta commande pour un début .......car je te rassure ........si tu y prends goût .....aux recettes de Valérie........à son humour anti dépresseur , à la Patisserie tout court ......tu es foutue ......tu vas augmenter les doses de chocolat à la prochaine commande ......tu risques peut-être même d&#39;en manquer avant ...... sans parler des oeufs , du beurre ......<br>et tu vas voir que ton mari va en redemander !<br>Mon budget pâtisserie a beaucoup augmenté mais le bonheur qui s&#39;ensuit aussi alors je préfère faire attention sur d&#39;autres choses ....<br>Eclates toi et tiens nous au courant :)))))<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3152302407900677436\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3152302407900677436-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3152302407900677436-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3152302407900677436-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3152302407900677436\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3152302407900677436-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c3011321059438561954-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3011321059438561954\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3011321059438561954-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6706661421386060386\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Nat</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395159392701#c6706661421386060386\">18 mars, 2014 17:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je me demandais quoi faire comme gâteau demain ...... J&#39;ai trouvé !!! Mon fils (8 ans ), me tanne pour faire le &quot;nutella &quot; maison !!! Bonne soirée <br><br><br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6706661421386060386\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6706661421386060386\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6706661421386060386-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6706661421386060386-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6706661421386060386-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6706661421386060386\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6706661421386060386-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4439210314790399529\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395162536727#c4439210314790399529\">18 mars, 2014 18:08</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour<br><br>J&#39;ai découvert ton blog y&#39;a pas longtemps et je dois dire que j&#39;en suis dingue! on se régale à chaque fois grâce à toi ! <br><br>Il faut absolument que j&#39;essaye ce gâteau ! mais avant je voulais te demander si le fait d&#39;avoir zapper l&#39;étape arrosage n&#39;a pas changer la texture qu&#39;il devrait avoir? et si c&#39;était possible d&#39;arroser avec un sirop normal plutôt qu&#39;avec le rhum ?<br><br>Merci d&#39;avance, j&#39;ai hâte de dévorer toutes tes autres recettes ! Sophia </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4439210314790399529\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4439210314790399529\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4439210314790399529-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4439210314790399529-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4535158099913700841\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395163474401#c4535158099913700841\">18 mars, 2014 18:24</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">En fait je ne la connais pas, la texture qu&#39;il devrait avoir... ;) Mais c&#39;est sûr qu&#39;avec le sirop il doit être bien imbibé. Mais il est déjà ultra fondant sans, alors ça ne m&#39;a pas posé problème. Par contre je ne vous conseille pas de faire un sirop, ça serait trop sucré !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4535158099913700841\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4535158099913700841-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4535158099913700841-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4535158099913700841-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4535158099913700841\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4535158099913700841-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5288115682020964478\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Sophia</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395830429138#c5288115682020964478\">26 mars, 2014 11:40</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Voilà je l&#39;ai fait, j&#39;ai suivi ta recette à la lettre et c&#39;était parfait! J&#39;ai déjà envie de le refaire ! Merci encore pour tes petites merveilles </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5288115682020964478\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5288115682020964478-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"th