f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395217111673#c2619318261688084250\">19 mars, 2014 09:18</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Pourquoi pas, si vous aimez ça ! Mais je ne connais pas la quantité, il ne faudrait pas que ça soit trop dosé. Mettez-en un peu et goûtez la pâte crue pour ajuster.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2619318261688084250\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2619318261688084250-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2619318261688084250-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2619318261688084250-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2619318261688084250\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2619318261688084250-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6384639216265295161\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">hanan</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395233265728#c6384639216265295161\">19 mars, 2014 13:47</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">ok , vous avez raison je vais gouter avant pour ajuster .......Merci.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6384639216265295161\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6384639216265295161-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6384639216265295161-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6384639216265295161-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6384639216265295161\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6384639216265295161-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6967100424275034515\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">hanan</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395414349564#c6967100424275034515\">21 mars, 2014 16:05</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Excellent gateau fait pour mon mari qui adore les gateaux a base d&#39;amande , juste un ptit soucis avec le glaçage qui etait trop liquide et que j&#39;ai du refaire car le gateau l &#39;avait absorbé ,du coup le gateau etait un peu trop sucré mais tres tres bon ....Merci Valerie,il fait parti de mes favoris!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6967100424275034515\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6967100424275034515-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6967100424275034515-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6967100424275034515-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6967100424275034515\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6967100424275034515-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3164527180833208867\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395650808853#c3164527180833208867\">24 mars, 2014 09:46</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Valérie, penses aux patinautes musulmans dans tes prochaines recettes, on mange pas de porc et on boit pas d&#39;alcool, que du halal alhamdoulillah sinon t&#39;auras moins de 70% de patinautes qui viennent sur ton site :)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3164527180833208867\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3164527180833208867-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3164527180833208867-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3164527180833208867-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3164527180833208867\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3164527180833208867-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c688613244967150548-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"688613244967150548\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c688613244967150548-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1762568895691132331\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">assia</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395181530038#c1762568895691132331\">18 mars, 2014 23:25</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir Valerie, comme promis apres les cookies, j&#39;ai teste ce magnifique gateau !!!!!! je ne sait plus quels adjecifs donnes ....je crois qu&#39;il faudrait en inventer d&#39;autres c&#39;est vraiment urgent ;)<br>Je l&#39;ai realise sans rhum mais j&#39;ai suivi ton conseil et la gousse de vanille ne l&#39;emporte pas du tout sur l&#39;amande au contraire, je jurerais qu&#39;elle rehausse son gout......la verite si j&#39;mens c&#39;etait divin !!!!!!!!! J&#39;ai juste eu un petit pepin au niveau du glacage, il etait liquide et le gateau l&#39;a absorbe. Au niveau des proportions, j&#39;ai mis 100g de sucre et 100g de beurre pour un moule de 19 cm de diametre et une petit moule a cake individuel. J&#39;ai coupe le gateau en 12 parts et je n&#39;en ai mange qu&#39;une et j&#39;en ai laisse une pour demain. Monsieur et Bonhomme se sont regales ;)<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1762568895691132331\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1762568895691132331\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1762568895691132331-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1762568895691132331-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1762568895691132331-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1762568895691132331\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1762568895691132331-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5086366194809590139\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">hali</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395215958163#c5086366194809590139\">19 mars, 2014 08:59</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour,<br>quand j&#39;ai vu les photos du gateau, je n&#39;ai pas pu résister, j&#39;avais lu ailleurs que pour une version sans alcool, on pouvait remplacer par du jus de citron ou d&#39;orange, ce que j&#39;ai fait, c&#39;était parfait et vraiment super bon, le citron va vraiment bien avec l&#39;amande, j&#39;en reviens pas tellement il est fondant.. on a trop aimé, par contre je doublerais les proportions la prochaine fois pour un effet visuel encore plus beau, tant pis pour les kilos ;-) et merci beaucoup...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5086366194809590139\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5086366194809590139\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5086366194809590139-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5086366194809590139-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c83861194651031828\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395217156840#c83861194651031828\">19 mars, 2014 09:19</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">En fait traditionnellement il doit être plat. Mais vous pouvez doubler, en le cuisant à 150&#176; et en prolongeant bien la cuisson.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/83861194651031828\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c83861194651031828-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c83861194651031828-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c83861194651031828-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"83861194651031828\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c83861194651031828-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c5086366194809590139-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5086366194809590139\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5086366194809590139-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1183439399891562368\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Jean-Edouard</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395224736539#c1183439399891562368\">19 mars, 2014 11:25</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Pourquoi évoquer sans cesse l&#39;apport calorique des gâteaux ? <br><br>Faites comme moi, si vous faites au déjeuner, un gâteau nantais pour le dessert , ne mangez qu&#39;une moitié de Paris Brest au goûter (celui de Ph Conticini bien sur !)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1183439399891562368\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1183439399891562368\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1183439399891562368-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1183439399891562368-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7952988614212394816\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395225983291#c7952988614212394816\">19 mars, 2014 11:46</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Avec une fondue savoyarde au p&#39;tit déj, c&#39;est parfait.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7952988614212394816\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7952988614212394816-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7952988614212394816-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7952988614212394816-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7952988614212394816\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7952988614212394816-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c1183439399891562368-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1183439399891562368\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1183439399891562368-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6075488224539415781\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">julie47</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395237173691#c6075488224539415781\">19 mars, 2014 14:52</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ayéééééé<br><br>fait et déjà dévoré par toute la famille...<br>Même pas eu le temps de le prendre en photo!<br><br>Je l&#39;ai fait dans un moule de 24 cm, j&#39;aurai du enlever un peu de temps de cuisson, il était un poil trop cuit et donc trop sec. Par contre mon glaçage n&#39;était pas aussi blanc et épais que le tiens, tu y repasse plusieurs fois?<br>La prochaine fois j&#39;essayerai de l&#39;arroser avant le glacage pour voir...<br>Même mon fils de 3 ans a adoré! alors pour te dire!<br><br>Merci encore pour cette belle (et horriblement bonne) recette!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6075488224539415781\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6075488224539415781\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6075488224539415781-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6075488224539415781-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6075488224539415781-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6075488224539415781\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6075488224539415781-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4692741028854040620\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395297599722#c4692741028854040620\">20 mars, 2014 07:39</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie, ne pouvant consommer d&#39;alcool, pourriez vous me dire si je peux et par quoi je pourrais remplacer le rhum du gateau nantais? Et à quelle dose? Merci pour vos réponses et un grand merci pour ce magnifique blog ainsi que pour ces photos qui donnent très envie. Bonne journée à vous.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4692741028854040620\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4692741028854040620\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4692741028854040620-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4692741028854040620-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4692741028854040620-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4692741028854040620\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4692741028854040620-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5755347108856851849\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//1.bp.blogspot.com/-6vuUc5BLA3I/Uv3FcZIUnpI/AAAAAAAAIpM/ZYtZyiH4TcE/s35/*\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/17431405366693406110\" rel=\"nofollow\">JPPreaux</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395320326187#c5755347108856851849\">20 mars, 2014 13:58</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Belle recette !<br>Je n&#39;ai pas réussi mon glaçage...<br>Utilisé du rhum brun...mieux avec du blanc <br>Glaçage trop liquide. Augmenter la quantité de sucre ou réduire celle de rhum...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5755347108856851849\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-1226236201\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5755347108856851849\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5755347108856851849-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5755347108856851849-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5755347108856851849-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5755347108856851849\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5755347108856851849-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9126764852707338720\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395321497973#c9126764852707338720\">20 mars, 2014 14:18</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Vous avez raison Jean-Pierre, je vais rectifier pour le glaçage.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9126764852707338720\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9126764852707338720\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9126764852707338720-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9126764852707338720-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c9126764852707338720-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9126764852707338720\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9126764852707338720-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1464890631065725695\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Jean-Edouard</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395322812571#c1464890631065725695\">20 mars, 2014 14:40</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Un petit commentaire pour poursuivre sur le Chocolat Valrhona. J&#39;ai visité l&#39;entreprise de Tain l&#39;Hermitage (dans le Drôme) l&#39;année dernière ... ce qui est formidable c&#39;est qu&#39;on peut aller faire d&#39;autres achats en sortant de la boutique ... quelque exemples : Hermitage, Saint Joseph, Crozes Hermitage, Cornas.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1464890631065725695\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1464890631065725695\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1464890631065725695-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1464890631065725695-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1464890631065725695-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1464890631065725695\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1464890631065725695-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1452244370588516316\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Nat</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395328571575#c1452244370588516316\">20 mars, 2014 16:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Hello Valérie, recette testée auprès de mes petites collègues ......... C&#39;est une tuerie disent elles !! <br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1452244370588516316\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1452244370588516316\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1452244370588516316-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1452244370588516316-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1452244370588516316-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1452244370588516316\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1452244370588516316-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c887842210073136794\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiRkyChC6cIxQCdkKJaCJ5s0cX1ne9eVCHDgX34lgeWBm82r4VNdz_tQT1gtIf9VL61WwGaXmAf-0NpyuAC9pJrZebors9sDWy30E9MZ4P2ckNp4VyUtvSih1Ubqi1y-XM/s45-c/image.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/07938037982324788857\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mag</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395349924762#c887842210073136794\">20 mars, 2014 22:12</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">cata, drame, horreur. Comme vous le disiez j&#39;ai failli partir mais ne jamais revenir ;)<br>J&#39;ai fait ma préparation avec mon Ken cooking chef et le fouet ballon avant d&#39;y insérer la poudre d&#39;amandes et la farine la pâte semblait &quot;caillée&quot; grumeleuse et pas lisse. <br>A quoi pensez vous que ce soit du ?? <br>Heureusement au final après cuisson le gâteau est très très bon. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"887842210073136794\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-986848894\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/887842210073136794\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c887842210073136794-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c887842210073136794-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6969155298111468599\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395427410883#c6969155298111468599\">21 mars, 2014 19:43</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Le mélange a grainé. C&#39;est ce qui arrive lorsque les oeufs sont froids. Tous les ingrédients doivent être à la même température lorsque l&#39;on fait un gâteau, c&#39;est pour cela que j&#39;ai précisé que les oeufs devaient être à température ambiante. Mais ce n&#39;est pas très grave rassurez-vous. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6969155298111468599\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6969155298111468599-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6969155298111468599-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6969155298111468599-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6969155298111468599\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6969155298111468599-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1725505462328615148\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiRkyChC6cIxQCdkKJaCJ5s0cX1ne9eVCHDgX34lgeWBm82r4VNdz_tQT1gtIf9VL61WwGaXmAf-0NpyuAC9pJrZebors9sDWy30E9MZ4P2ckNp4VyUtvSih1Ubqi1y-XM/s45-c/image.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/07938037982324788857\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mag</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395435465762#c1725505462328615148\">21 mars, 2014 21:57</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Pourtant mes œufs étaient à température ambiante j&#39;ai suivi vos conseils ils logent désormais dans le cellier. Peux être la vitesse max ou le fouet ballon du cooking chef... En tout cas mille mercis pour vos superbes recettes et pour avoir fait de moi une nouvelle sportive depuis 2 mois. J&#39;ai repris le sport c&#39;était soit ça soit changer de garde robe ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-986848894\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1725505462328615148\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1725505462328615148-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1725505462328615148-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1725505462328615148-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1725505462328615148\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1725505462328615148-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4499977337611834472\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395435943216#c4499977337611834472\">21 mars, 2014 22:05</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Normalement si ça graine c&#39;est qu&#39;il y a une différence de température entre le beurre et les oeufs. Ca m&#39;étonne que ce soit le fouet. Bizarre... <br>Je crois que je vais aller courir aussi... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4499977337611834472\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4499977337611834472-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4499977337611834472-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4499977337611834472-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4499977337611834472\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4499977337611834472-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c887842210073136794-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"887842210073136794\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c887842210073136794-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1820042565864524890\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Nadia</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395355422117#c1820042565864524890\">20 mars, 2014 23:43</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valerie, je n&#39;utilise que du beurre non sale. Et etant au Canada, je n&#39;ai jamais trouve de beurre demi-sel. Quelle quantite de sel conseillez-vous donc que j&#39;utilise pour cette recette ? J&#39;adoooooore tous les gateaux a base d&#39;amande, il me tarde vraiment de faire celui-ci ! Merci de partager tous ces delices ! Et j&#39;adore votre style aussi !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1820042565864524890\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1820042565864524890\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1820042565864524890-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1820042565864524890-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3767531458331020950\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395427499939#c3767531458331020950\">21 mars, 2014 19:44</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Une demi cuillère à café suffira je pense.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3767531458331020950\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3767531458331020950-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3767531458331020950-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3767531458331020950-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3767531458331020950\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3767531458331020950-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c1820042565864524890-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1820042565864524890\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1820042565864524890-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6892676732314154702\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395392855914#c6892676732314154702\">21 mars, 2014 10:07</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">j&#39;attends ce we pour le faire, j&#39;ai hâte des bises;</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6892676732314154702\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6892676732314154702\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6892676732314154702-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6892676732314154702-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6892676732314154702-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6892676732314154702\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6892676732314154702-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c661493745346367311\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Mirna</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395414287877#c661493745346367311\">21 mars, 2014 16:04</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">C&#39;était supeeeeer bon !!! Le goût m&#39;a fait penser à de la frangipane que j&#39;adore d&#39;ailleurs. Mais j&#39;ai su rester raisonnable et après une petite part, tout le reste a été dévoré par mes collègues..ainsi que celle au régime. <br>J&#39;ai osé mettre les 20 gr de rhum à la sortie du four en plus. Tout le monde a adoré. J&#39; avais peur que ce soit trop alcoolisé mais en fait vu qu&#39;on le met sur le gâteau chaud on n&#39;a plus le goût de l&#39;alcool mais uniquement l&#39;arôme du rhum. En plus je suis de la Martinique, je me fais toujours un stock pour la pâtisserie quand j&#39;y vais on quand ma famille vient et je trouve que le parfum de nos rhums sont juste irremplaçables. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"661493745346367311\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/661493745346367311\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c661493745346367311-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c661493745346367311-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3893291355263762668\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395427594245#c3893291355263762668\">21 mars, 2014 19:46</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Si même celle au régime a succombé... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3893291355263762668\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3893291355263762668-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3893291355263762668-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3893291355263762668-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3893291355263762668\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3893291355263762668-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c661493745346367311-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"661493745346367311\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c661493745346367311-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6906205652332968321\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Isa la levure</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395418506849#c6906205652332968321\">21 mars, 2014 17:15</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">C&#39;est super bon, c&#39;est une pâtisserie que je fais souvent en version individuelle (je ne sais pas si tu avais vu la finale du combat des régions, sur la 6, une candidate nantaise les avais faits, et Lignac lui avait carrément demandé sa recette).<br> Il ne faut pas du tout mettre le nez dedans, c&#39;est addictif. On peut jouer avec la recette, pour un de mes fils (toujours en version individuelle), je fais le bounty inversé, je remplace la poudre d&#39;amande par de la noix de coco, et un gros morceau de chocolat noir dedans. <br>Je vois que la pâtisserie revient sur le site...... ça démange hein !!! gros bisous</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6906205652332968321\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6906205652332968321\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6906205652332968321-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6906205652332968321-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7478527208156510659\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395427570537#c7478527208156510659\">21 mars, 2014 19:46</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mais tu as toujours des idées de malade !!! Quelle bonne idée de remplacer la poudre d&#39;amande par la noix de coco ! Ca doit être super aussi de faire un glaçage au choco pour la version individuelle ! Punaise il faut que j&#39;essaie ! </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7478527208156510659\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7478527208156510659-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7478527208156510659-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7478527208156510659-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7478527208156510659\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7478527208156510659-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2608801537256649043\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Isa la levure</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395498280765#c2608801537256649043\">22 mars, 2014 15:24</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Glaçage au chocolat je n&#39;y avais pas pensé, là c&#39;est du Bounty.... c&#39;était quoi la recette de base déjà.......................... parce que j&#39;ai aussi de la poudre de pistache</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2608801537256649043\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2608801537256649043-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2608801537256649043-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2608801537256649043-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2608801537256649043\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2608801537256649043-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8406205786060386664\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">assia</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395691976234#c8406205786060386664\">24 mars, 2014 21:12</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir Mesdames, J&#39;ai teste la version bounty et il etat tres bon mais je prefere nettement la version originale ....Merci Isa la levure pour cette idee</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8406205786060386664\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8406205786060386664-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8406205786060386664-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8406205786060386664-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8406205786060386664\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8406205786060386664-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6906205652332968321-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6906205652332968321\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6906205652332968321-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7526100238913662907\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">samantha</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395424794507#c7526100238913662907\">21 mars, 2014 18:59</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Le gateau est au four! L odeur qu il dégage donne envie de ne pas attendre la fin du miniteur!<br>J ai hâte d y gouter :)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7526100238913662907\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7526100238913662907\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7526100238913662907-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7526100238913662907-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7526100238913662907-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7526100238913662907\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7526100238913662907-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7190530696580625936\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Vérone</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395428586809#c7190530696580625936\">21 mars, 2014 20:03</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Fichtre! la belle bête ! merci pour cette découverte savoureuse ! j&#39;ai quand même guetté, quand mon petit de 3 ans 1/2 a quitté la table du goûter, s&#39;il ne tanguait pas un peu, vu qu&#39;il s&#39;est enfilé deux parts de suite (petites) (mais bon). Non non. Ou bien il tient l&#39;alcool ou le dosage réduit est parfait ! <br>Par contre... c&#39;est foutu. Je suis obligée de tester, pff, pratiquement chaque nouvelle recette. Il est trop bien ce blog !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7190530696580625936\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7190530696580625936\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7190530696580625936-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7190530696580625936-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7190530696580625936-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7190530696580625936\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7190530696580625936-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3694953770397301639\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Delphine2B</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395476414615#c3694953770397301639\">22 mars, 2014 09:20</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Voilà j&#39;ai du en faire un 2ème hier , j&#39;avais pas le choix , c&#39;était comme un appel ; mais je n&#39;y ai pas encore touché car je le trouve meilleur quand il a 2 ou 3 jours.<br>Et puis aussi j&#39;ai fait un opéra pour la 1 ère fois pour mon cher mari qui m&#39;en réclamait un depuis que j&#39;ai découvert ton blog......on le goûtera ce soir avec nos amis .<br>J&#39;ai de la pâte à brioche Tangzhong qui pousse dans mon frigo ; j&#39;ai de quoi faire 2 brioches , j&#39;ai prévu en congeler une car le résultat est pas mal du tout , ma petite a bien apprécié pour son petit dej !<br>je me demande si je ne vais pas m&#39;attaquer à faire des buns pour ce soir .... </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3694953770397301639\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3694953770397301639\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3694953770397301639-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3694953770397301639-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3694953770397301639-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3694953770397301639\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3694953770397301639-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8394714361468273622\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">anne</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395507753429#c8394714361468273622\">22 mars, 2014 18:02</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">génial j&#39; en suis à mon deuxième ( bye bye le maillot et la petite robe que j ai acheté trop petite en espérant maigrir)<br>par contre j ai imbibé à chaud et c était super !!!<br>merci merci je teste toutes vos recettes</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8394714361468273622\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8394714361468273622\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8394714361468273622-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8394714361468273622-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8394714361468273622-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8394714361468273622\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8394714361468273622-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c9177626301605762770\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"http://caprices-gourmands.fr\" rel=\"nofollow\">Camille | Caprices Gourmands</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395523349896#c9177626301605762770\">22 mars, 2014 22:22</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Zut, j&#39;ai vraiment tenté de résister et de ne pas ouvrir l&#39;article ! <br>Trop tard, je me sens obligé de le faire, tout le monde en parle :p<br><br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9177626301605762770\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/9177626301605762770\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c9177626301605762770-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c9177626301605762770-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c9177626301605762770-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"9177626301605762770\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c9177626301605762770-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5441977790529923660\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395527195779#c5441977790529923660\">22 mars, 2014 23:26</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir Valérie,<br>j&#39;ai testé une version avec confiture d&#39;abricot entre le glaçage et le gâteau mes garçons adorent j&#39;ai vu cette variante sur le site &quot;patiss.com&quot;<br>Au vu de ton blog il y a une recette toujours sur ce site qui a sa place sur ton blog c&#39;est le &quot;fraîcheur du verger&quot; pomme citron un grand succès à chaque fois que je le fais.<br>Merci pour toutes ces recettes, ces commentaires je m&#39;éclate en cuisine.<br>Damien</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5441977790529923660\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5441977790529923660\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5441977790529923660-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5441977790529923660-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5441977790529923660-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5441977790529923660\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5441977790529923660-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6136464650657478757\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395530273423#c6136464650657478757\">23 mars, 2014 00:17</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Salut ! Purée mais qu&#39;il est bon ce gâteau ! Je l&#39;ai fait il y a un moi pour l&#39;anniv&#39; d&#39;une personne qui aime le rhum ! Il en a mangé la moitié...quand je lui dit la composition...il a comment dire un PEU regretter ! Comme il dit c&#39;est pas tout les jours !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6136464650657478757\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6136464650657478757\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6136464650657478757-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6136464650657478757-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6136464650657478757-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6136464650657478757\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6136464650657478757-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c799014792732811324\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395621373204#c799014792732811324\">24 mars, 2014 01:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">J&#8217;ai souri en voyant la recette sur le blog.<br>Nos esprits se sont rejoints parce que j&#8217;ai fais le gâteau samedi.<br>J&#8217;hésitais à le faire parce que je pensais que c&#8217;était un gâteau &#171; lourd &#187; mais pas du tout, il fond dans la bouche. Un régal.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"799014792732811324\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/799014792732811324\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c799014792732811324-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c799014792732811324-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c799014792732811324-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"799014792732811324\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c799014792732811324-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2064015290108364467\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Dorothée FF</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395649538544#c2064015290108364467\">24 mars, 2014 09:25</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">C&#39;est un gateau d&#39;autant plus excellent qu&#39;il est d&#39;une simplicité déroutante. J&#39;ai en revanche doublé les proportions du glaçage... Le gateau d&#39;anniversaire que mon petit Roi Balthazar amènera à l&#39;école est tout trouvé !! (oui je sais il y a du Rhum...so What ? ils dormiront bien...)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2064015290108364467\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2064015290108364467\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2064015290108364467-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2064015290108364467-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4808403075194329654\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395661545443#c4808403075194329654\">24 mars, 2014 12:45</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Dorothée c&#39;est pas sympa pour le rhum :(.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4808403075194329654\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4808403075194329654-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4808403075194329654-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4808403075194329654-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4808403075194329654\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4808403075194329654-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c2064015290108364467-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2064015290108364467\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2064015290108364467-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8488427870433359576\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Miss k</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395671930781#c8488427870433359576\">24 mars, 2014 15:38</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour tout le monde, <br><br>Valérie, ce gateau est une tuerie, comme la pate à tartiner de notre cri cri d&#39;amour, et toutes les recettes de ton blog que j&#39;essaie.<br>Question: quel Rhum utilisez vous? En Martiniquaise que je suis, je vous suggère le &quot;Grand Arôme &quot; du Gallion. Ce n&#39;est pas un grand cru, loin de là! mais pour la cuisine et la patisserie c&#39;est le must car le gout est très fort (donc à utiliser avec parcimonie) et qu&#39;à la moindre chaleur, le taux d&#39;alcool s&#39;évapore !!! Si vous ne le trouvez pas, préférez le rhum vieux (pas ambré) au rhum blanc. <br><br>Merci en tout cas de tous ces &quot;bons pour 10 kg sur la Balance !!!!!&quot;<br><br>Dans l&#39;attente d&#39;un bon supplémentaire ,<br><br>A bientôt , <br><br>miss Ca</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8488427870433359576\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8488427870433359576\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8488427870433359576-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8488427870433359576-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8280448260804917394\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Sebneb</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395693648311#c8280448260804917394\">24 mars, 2014 21:40</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir,<br>De mon côté, le gâteau est en train de cuire. Pour le rhum, j&#39;ai utilisé du Negrita.<br>La pate crue est déjà une tuerie...<br><br>Valérie, je n&#39;ai pas vu sur ton super blog la recette des sablés très chocolat à la fleur de sel de Pierre Hermé. Ils sont vraiment super bons, je te conseille d&#39;essayer si tu n&#39;as pas encore testé. Moi j&#39;y ai adhéré.<br>sebneb</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8280448260804917394\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8280448260804917394-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c828044826