ybox-single\" id=\"c3983409881226007799-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7194448833098094468\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395733733739#c7194448833098094468\">25 mars, 2014 08:48</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">@Miss K : Merci beaucoup pour ces renseignements sur le rhum ! Je n&#39;y connais rien, alors je note... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7194448833098094468\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7194448833098094468-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7194448833098094468-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7194448833098094468-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7194448833098094468\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7194448833098094468-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8802574469367180544\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">sebneb</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395738610162#c8802574469367180544\">25 mars, 2014 10:10</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">autant pour moi alors... Ouf car ils sont vraiment excellents. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8802574469367180544\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8802574469367180544-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8802574469367180544-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8802574469367180544-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8802574469367180544\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8802574469367180544-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8252788999744223206\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395738962207#c8252788999744223206\">25 mars, 2014 10:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Oui, ils sont magnifiques !!! </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8252788999744223206\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8252788999744223206-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8252788999744223206-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8252788999744223206-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8252788999744223206\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8252788999744223206-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c8488427870433359576-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8488427870433359576\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8488427870433359576-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c141009082790175649\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Johanna</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395697374065#c141009082790175649\">24 mars, 2014 22:42</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir Valérie,<br>Merci pour cette recette que tout le monde a apprécié. <br>Il était par contre un peu trop compact. As tu une astuce pour qu&#39;il soit plus aérée comme le tien qui est soit dit en passant magnifique ??? <br><br>Bonne soirée </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"141009082790175649\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/141009082790175649\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c141009082790175649-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c141009082790175649-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3936133157855820518\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395733555409#c3936133157855820518\">25 mars, 2014 08:45</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Mais c&#39;est un gâteau compact. Par contre il faut bien crémer le beurre et le sucre, et bien fouetter après chaque oeuf. En revanche il ne lèvera pas trop, c&#39;est normal. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3936133157855820518\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3936133157855820518-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3936133157855820518-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3936133157855820518-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3936133157855820518\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3936133157855820518-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4542827888433060482\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Johanna</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396133584351#c4542827888433060482\">29 mars, 2014 23:53</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ah d&#39;accord. Merci beaucoup pour ta réponse. Je crois que je n&#39;est jamais autant crémer j&#39;ai même penser que j&#39;avait tout raté parce qu&#39;on avait l&#39;impression que ca avait caillé !!! J&#39;était tellement paniquée et je me suis dit bon on verra bien ! ;) <br><br>Bonne soirée </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4542827888433060482\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4542827888433060482-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4542827888433060482-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4542827888433060482-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4542827888433060482\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4542827888433060482-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c141009082790175649-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"141009082790175649\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c141009082790175649-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2070621061437500001\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395744219055#c2070621061437500001\">25 mars, 2014 11:43</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">fannygriotte<br>punaise c&#39;est vrais qu&#39;il est bon, y en reste plus une miette, ils ont tous mangé </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2070621061437500001\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2070621061437500001\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2070621061437500001-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2070621061437500001-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2070621061437500001-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2070621061437500001\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2070621061437500001-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5608081300820502\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/15171487224526705788\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unknown</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395749461675#c5608081300820502\">25 mars, 2014 13:11</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Et oui c&#39;est vrai ........une vrai tuerie !!! si je peux donner mon avis, mouillez le gâteaux encore un peu tiède.Perso j&#39;ai fais un sirop avec 150 gr d&#39;eau et 75 gr de sucre et une fois refroidi ajouter alors 40 gr de rhum. Mouiller des deux côtés idem du &quot;Voyageur&quot;. Vous n&#39;êtes pas obligé de mettre tout le sirop. Encore merci pour cette suculente recette</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5608081300820502\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-575142434\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5608081300820502\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5608081300820502-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5608081300820502-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5608081300820502-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5608081300820502\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5608081300820502-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6519969909491417020\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">la fouine</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395839268424#c6519969909491417020\">26 mars, 2014 14:07</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">chez moi, personne n&#39;aime le goût du rhum..... Croyez-vous que je peux utiliser du vin blanc à la place???</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6519969909491417020\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6519969909491417020\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6519969909491417020-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6519969909491417020-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6519969909491417020-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6519969909491417020\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6519969909491417020-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1642714188885243090\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395840301560#c1642714188885243090\">26 mars, 2014 14:25</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Surtout pas de vin blanc pour la pâtisserie.<br>Par contre vous pouvez mettre :<br>- du jus d&#39;orange et des zests<br>- du jus de citron et des zests<br>- les graines d&#39;une belle gousse de vanille<br>- de la fleur d&#39;oranger</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1642714188885243090\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1642714188885243090\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1642714188885243090-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1642714188885243090-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7594677395735352835\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">la fouine</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395847169109#c7594677395735352835\">26 mars, 2014 16:19</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ah bon pas de vin blanc pour la pâtisserie???? Mais???? Ma grand -mère me fait régulièrement un gâteau au vin blanc et j&#39;adore ça....<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7594677395735352835\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7594677395735352835-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7594677395735352835-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7594677395735352835-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7594677395735352835\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7594677395735352835-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5438488855311364226\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395848779351#c5438488855311364226\">26 mars, 2014 16:46</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Vous venez de m&#39;apprendre quelque chose...<br>Quoi qu&#39;il en soit cela ne conviendra pas ici.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5438488855311364226\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5438488855311364226-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5438488855311364226-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5438488855311364226-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5438488855311364226\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5438488855311364226-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c1642714188885243090-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1642714188885243090\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1642714188885243090-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c472511588775666238\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Lou</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395840806138#c472511588775666238\">26 mars, 2014 14:33</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie,<br>et encore une recette à essayer ; mais cela devient dur de suivre le rythme. Mais celle là je me suis dit qu&#39;il fallait que je la fasses absolument et je l&#39;ai mise sur le dessus de la pile des recettes à essayer. Tu parles d&#39;une version sans farine. pourrais-tu me la donner ou alors faut-il simplement remplacer la farine par le même poids en poudre d&#39;amandes? merci</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"472511588775666238\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/472511588775666238\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c472511588775666238-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c472511588775666238-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3839887385546197812\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395905870339#c3839887385546197812\">27 mars, 2014 08:37</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">En fait il faut mettre plus de poudre d&#39;amande (150g) et moins de beurre (80g).</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3839887385546197812\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3839887385546197812-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3839887385546197812-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3839887385546197812-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3839887385546197812\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3839887385546197812-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c472511588775666238-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"472511588775666238\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c472511588775666238-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2470817809151316710\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395853906202#c2470817809151316710\">26 mars, 2014 18:11</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Coucou Valérie, il cuit ......... je ne sais si je vais pouvoir attendre jusqu&#39;à demain ..... :-( quel supplice au secours ;-))))) Myriam miam miam </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2470817809151316710\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2470817809151316710\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2470817809151316710-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2470817809151316710-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2470817809151316710-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2470817809151316710\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2470817809151316710-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7706360975658281641\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">nathalie</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395914330156#c7706360975658281641\">27 mars, 2014 10:58</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour, ça fait un moment que je voulais vous remercier pour votre humour, votre sens de l&#39;esthétique et vos fabuleuses recettes. J&#39;en ai testé pas mal et félicitations pour le partage.<br>J&#39;ai un petit commentaire à faire sur le gâteau nantais, je l&#39;ai fais hier en respectant la recette à la lettre. J&#39;ai un moule rond que j&#39;ai mesuré (cool, 22 cm, parfait). <br>Mais je n&#39;avais pas assez de pâte pour le remplir, j&#39;ai donc dû faire un bricolage avec un cercle plus petit, j&#39;ai un peu galéré.La prochaine fois je doublerais les quantités, pareil pour le glaçage, il en manquait.<br>Sinon c&#39;est vrai que c&#39;est délicieux. <br>Je testerai la version aux pistaches ce week end.<br>Merci aussi pour les explications détaillées.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7706360975658281641\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7706360975658281641\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7706360975658281641-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7706360975658281641-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2229710807396498717\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395914942410#c2229710807396498717\">27 mars, 2014 11:09</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Merci beaucoup. Je vais alors indiquer qu&#39;il vaut mieux utiliser un moule de 20cm, contrairement à ce que dit la recette originale.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2229710807396498717\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2229710807396498717-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2229710807396498717-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2229710807396498717-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2229710807396498717\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2229710807396498717-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1330126928958967867\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396791840873#c1330126928958967867\">06 avril, 2014 15:44</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">désolé , recette faite avec un moule de 24 cm et bien assez de pâte , il faut juste réduire le temps de cuisson à 35 mn th6 !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1330126928958967867\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1330126928958967867-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1330126928958967867-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1330126928958967867-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1330126928958967867\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1330126928958967867-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c7706360975658281641-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7706360975658281641\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7706360975658281641-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3982457873223804310\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">lou</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1395935574132#c3982457873223804310\">27 mars, 2014 16:52</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Cool,<br>comme çà je vais pouvoir le tester pendant la semaine de Pessah et après je le referai avec la farine et je comparerai. merci Valérie</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3982457873223804310\">Répondre</a><span clas