><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1724289210729685859-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1724289210729685859-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1724289210729685859\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1724289210729685859-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6305467620942561805\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Choupette</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396125182234#c6305467620942561805\">29 mars, 2014 21:33</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie,<br>J&#39;adore cette recette et la version pistache est une idée géniale ! Une petite question concernant le cercle: faut-il un cercle à tarte ou un cercle à entremet ? Votre gâteau me semble trop haut pour un cercle à tarte mais c&#39;est peut-être la photo qui fait ça ?</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6305467620942561805\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6305467620942561805\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6305467620942561805-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6305467620942561805-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2420852443027995284\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396128891489#c2420852443027995284\">29 mars, 2014 22:34</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Un cercle à entremet, ou un moule, tout simplement ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2420852443027995284\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2420852443027995284-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2420852443027995284-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2420852443027995284-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2420852443027995284\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2420852443027995284-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6305467620942561805-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6305467620942561805\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6305467620942561805-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7413034921389605802\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Celine972</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396207495350#c7413034921389605802\">30 mars, 2014 21:24</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour<br>Aujourd&#39;hui j&#39;ai fait le gâteau nantais ET les feldettes... J&#39;en pleure d&#39;avance pour mon pèse personne, mais mes enfants sont ravis ! Ça doit faire une bonne quinzaine de recettes de ce blog que je teste, des simples et des moins simples, et c&#39;est toujours un succès... Maintenant quand mon fils me dit &quot;maman pour mon anniversaire je voudrais que tu me fasses un opéra&quot;, même pas peur... Un p&#180;tit tour ici, et hop ! Ça roule !<br>Une seule recette me résiste encore et toujours : les macarons... Mais un prochain essai est prévu mercredi (avec les blancs des feldettes)<br>Bref, merci pour toutes ces recettes aussi pédagogiques que caloriques !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7413034921389605802\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7413034921389605802\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7413034921389605802-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7413034921389605802-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2948258640564478370\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Céline972</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396207930201#c2948258640564478370\">30 mars, 2014 21:32</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Ceci dit je rejoins miss k... Martiniquaise aussi, j&#39;utilise un rhum agricole vieux. Pour ma part un Depaz vieux, produit près de chez moi. Le Negrita ne trouvera jamais sa place dans ma cuisine... Quant au rhum blanc en pâtisserie, personnellement je ne le ferais pas... L&#39;arôme du rhum vieux est incomparable !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2948258640564478370\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2948258640564478370-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2948258640564478370-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2948258640564478370-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2948258640564478370\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2948258640564478370-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7949336080688907845\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396255973380#c7949336080688907845\">31 mars, 2014 10:52</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Merci pour toutes ces infos sur le rhum. Je le regarderai d&#39;un autre oeil maintenant... ;)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7949336080688907845\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7949336080688907845-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7949336080688907845-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7949336080688907845-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7949336080688907845\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7949336080688907845-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c7413034921389605802-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7413034921389605802\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7413034921389605802-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5712546762705845757\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396278917646#c5712546762705845757\">31 mars, 2014 17:15</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">testé ce week end pour un repas entre amis (chacun portait un plat) il a eu un grand succés. je confirme je l&#39;ai trouvé bien meilleur le lendemain. merci pour cette superbe recette comme d&#39;habitude. isabelle19</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5712546762705845757\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5712546762705845757\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5712546762705845757-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5712546762705845757-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5712546762705845757-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5712546762705845757\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5712546762705845757-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4062257088877575798\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/14654513953539475584\" rel=\"nofollow\">Séverine</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396774646631#c4062257088877575798\">06 avril, 2014 10:57</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie, j&#39;ai découvert ton blog il y a quelques temps et j&#39;en suis fan. J&#39;ai déjà testé les crêpes et je te confirme qu&#39;il s&#39;agit là de l&#39;ultime recette !!! Hier soir, méthode japonaise pour le pain mais euh..... loupé ! Je n&#39;ai ni four avec fonction étuve ni micro-ondes et j&#39;ai fait lever ma pâte à côté de la cheminée où il devait faire trop chaud .... Ce matin, gâteau nantais, il semble magnifique mais pas encore goûté. Par contre ça s&#39;est compliqué au moment du glaçage au fondant, un pur cauchemar !!!! Ça durcissait trop vite et je n&#39;avais pas le temps de l&#39;étaler sur mon gâteau ! Après 15 kg de sucre glace et 3 l de rhum, ça ressemble presque à quelque chose mais bon.......au secours, as-tu une astuce stp ?</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4062257088877575798\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-772929340\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4062257088877575798\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4062257088877575798-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4062257088877575798-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5405642253924657650\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396796582262#c5405642253924657650\">06 avril, 2014 17:03</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">coucou , moi je verse les 10 g de rhum en premier et je rajoute les 50 g de sucre glace (en même temps sur ma balance de cuisine) , je mélange et je verse au centre , étaler à la pointe du couteau , et je recommence car étant gourmande j&#39;en ai fait un plus grand , donc pas assez ... alors re-rhum + sucre glace et re-étalage au couteau pour finir , c&#39;est nickel !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5405642253924657650\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5405642253924657650-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5405642253924657650-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5405642253924657650-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5405642253924657650\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5405642253924657650-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c4062257088877575798-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4062257088877575798\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4062257088877575798-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5454032318698194651\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396791582254#c5454032318698194651\">06 avril, 2014 15:39</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">le temps de cuisson est trop long , 35 mn th 6 aurait été top ... pour moi !<br>pour une fois j&#39;ai voulu suivre à la lettre et le gâteau à crâmé dessous , j&#39;ai retiré le surplus de cuisson et ajouté 15g de rhum pou l&#39;imbiber , reste plus q&#39;à le glacer , on verra ce soir !<br>merci pour la recette que je réadapterais en cuisson la prochaine fois !!!<br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5454032318698194651\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5454032318698194651\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5454032318698194651-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5454032318698194651-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1312839424571154252\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396796252313#c1312839424571154252\">06 avril, 2014 16:57</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">aïe aïe aïe !!! même avec la sur-cuisson c&#39;est diviiiin !!!<br>je n&#39;ose même pas imaginé avec ces 10 mn de moins , que faire ? c&#39;est diabolique !!!<br>tu as entièrement raison : y goûter c&#39;est succomber !<br>il me tarde déjà de me refaire , et mon homme qui adore les gâteaux à base de rhum , je ne serais plus seulement de corvée de baba lol !!<br>j&#39;y retourne !!!!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1312839424571154252\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1312839424571154252-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1312839424571154252-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c1312839424571154252-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1312839424571154252\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c1312839424571154252-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3457388185945402444\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396875864186#c3457388185945402444\">07 avril, 2014 15:04</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">terrible , encore meilleur le lendemain !!! ce qui est super c&#39;est qu&#39;une fois qu&#39;on a la base on peut la refaire à toutes &quot;les sauces&quot; ... j&#39;imagine à l&#39;amaretto ou sans alcool à l&#39;orange , au citron ... miam miam ...<br>je vais tester de ce pas à l&#39;amaretto ! allez on y retourne !<br>c&#39;est pô bien ... mais bon il pleut ici , alors faut bien s&#39;occuper un ptit peu ...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3457388185945402444\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3457388185945402444-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3457388185945402444-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3457388185945402444-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3457388185945402444\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3457388185945402444-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c5454032318698194651-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5454032318698194651\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5454032318698194651-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c4093916532900812938\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Carochocolat</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1396979447420#c4093916532900812938\">08 avril, 2014 19:50</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonsoir Valérie,<br><br>J&#39;ai testé la recette et je dois dire que la texture est extraordinaire!!!<br>Par contre, y a un truc que je n&#39;ai pas compris...je ne bois jamais d&#39;alcool, et donc généralement, dès qu&#39;il y en a un tout petit peu dans une recette, je le sens immédiatement! Et là, j&#39;ai trouvé le rhum à peine perceptible (je n&#39;ai pas imbibé le gâteau après cuisson). Ca m&#39;intrigue...<br><br>Néanmoins recette à refaire avec des variantes! :) Merci Valérie!</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4093916532900812938\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/4093916532900812938\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c4093916532900812938-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c4093916532900812938-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c4093916532900812938-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"4093916532900812938\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c4093916532900812938-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6468874464642315562\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397226894095#c6468874464642315562\">11 avril, 2014 16:34</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour, je ne crois pas que quelqu&#39;un ait déjà fait la remarque : il me semble que ce gâteau est aussi connu sous le nom de &quot;Le Voyageur&quot;. Quel titre poétique pour ce gâteau qui a été conçu dans l&#39;optique d&#39;une conservation optimale, ainsi les voyageurs (d&#39;où son nom) pouvaient avoir des sucreries en provisions! Ce gâteau fut d&#39;ailleurs un sujet d&#39;épreuve dans l&#39;émission &quot;Le meilleur pâtissier&quot; animée par Mercotte et Cyril Lignac. A bon entendeur...</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6468874464642315562\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6468874464642315562\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6468874464642315562-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6468874464642315562-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3686365963022072237\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397230147505#c3686365963022072237\">11 avril, 2014 17:29</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Effectivement quelqu&#39;un en a déjà parlé ici, mais ce n&#39;est pas le voyageur. La recette est différente. Le voyageur est un gâteau à base de pâte d&#39;amande, qui contient seulement 50g de beurre, et qui contient également de la levure. Au final les textures ne sont pas du tout les mêmes.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3686365963022072237\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3686365963022072237-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3686365963022072237-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3686365963022072237-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3686365963022072237\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3686365963022072237-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c6468874464642315562-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6468874464642315562\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6468874464642315562-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c8696330809889200390\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397425987365#c8696330809889200390\">13 avril, 2014 23:53</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Une tuerie? Ben oui! Le premier trucidé a été le gâteau lui-même! Il ne connaîtra pas de deuxième jour et nous sommes donc totalement incapables de dire s&#39;il est meilleur le lendemain...<br>Comme nous ne sommes pas fans de glaçage, je me suis contenté de le saupoudrer de sucre glace après l&#39;avoir imbibé de 15 grammes de rhum à la sortie du four.<br>Excellent résultat. Attention à la cuisson, 35 minutes ont été suffisantes chez moi.<br>Un grand merci pour cette recette (et pour plein d&#39;autres aussi)!<br>Jean-Marc</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8696330809889200390\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/8696330809889200390\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c8696330809889200390-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c8696330809889200390-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c8696330809889200390-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"8696330809889200390\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c8696330809889200390-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2052841279382540758\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397650340287#c2052841279382540758\">16 avril, 2014 14:12</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour <br>Moi aussi je suis nantaise et je fais ce gâteaux très souvent a la maison vous pouvez le faire dans des petits moule et le servire avec le café<br>Un petit conseil sitôt sorti du four arroser avec le rhum <br>ps il y a pleins d&#39;autre recette nantaise <br>Bonne journée marie <br></p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2052841279382540758\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2052841279382540758\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2052841279382540758-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2052841279382540758-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2052841279382540758-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2052841279382540758\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2052841279382540758-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c260770172759079745\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03544222507346845840\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anne</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397810209128#c260770172759079745\">18 avril, 2014 10:36</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">bonjour, je viens de finir la préparation, j&#39;ai eu un petit souci... 1er essai réalisé au kitchenaid , beurre + sucre + oeufs et là catastrophe, j&#39;ai eu l&#39;impression que le mélange avait caillé !! j&#39;ai tout jeté et refais au batteur en battant moins vite et moins longtemps, la pâte avait un aspect un peu plus lisse. Rassurez moi Valérie, j&#39;ai eu raison de jeter ce mélange..granuleux ?? <br>Sinon j&#39;adore votre blog, j&#39;y passe des heures, c&#39;est un vrai bonheur et un vrai régal. <br>Anne</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"260770172759079745\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-958529473\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/260770172759079745\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c260770172759079745-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c260770172759079745-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6692415133496912383\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397812575061#c6692415133496912383\">18 avril, 2014 11:16</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Aïe aïe aïe...il ne fallait pas la jeter ! C&#39;est aspect n&#39;est pas grave du tout ! <br>Désolée... </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6692415133496912383\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6692415133496912383-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6692415133496912383-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6692415133496912383-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6692415133496912383\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6692415133496912383-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2374222662160785752\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//www.blogger.com/img/blogger_logo_round_35.png\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03544222507346845840\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anne</a></cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1397818237912#c2374222662160785752\">18 avril, 2014 12:50</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">pas grave... je le saurai pour la prochaine fois (qui risque d&#39;arriver assez vite...)j&#39;ai déjà méchamment englouti une partie de cette petite merveille ( j&#39;ai fait la version pistache) et là je sens l&#39;appel de mon vélo d&#39;appartement histoire de me donner bonne conscience avant de terminer le gateau ! A bientôt. Anne </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-958529473\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2374222662160785752\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2374222662160785752-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2374222662160785752-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2374222662160785752-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2374222662160785752\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2374222662160785752-ce\"></div></li></div><div id=\"c260770172759079745-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"260770172759079745\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c260770172759079745-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7795471432724748823\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Lysa</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1398249187462#c7795471432724748823\">23 avril, 2014 12:33</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Miammmmmmm !!!!!<br>En effet, il est encore meilleur le lendemain !<br>Par contre j&#39;ai eu des soucis pour le glaçage. D&#39;abord j&#39;ai utilisé du rhum brun, donc la couleur n&#39;était pas terrible. Ensuite, c&#39;était trop compact avec les proportions indiquées, il y a donc des miettes qui se sont arrachées et mélangées au glaçage.<br>N&#39;empêche, c&#39;est TROP bon !!! j&#39;ai ajouté les 20g de rhum sur le gâteau à la sortie du four, car on adore le rhum et franchement, c&#39;est très équilibré !</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7795471432724748823\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7795471432724748823\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7795471432724748823-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7795471432724748823-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7795471432724748823-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"7795471432724748823\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c7795471432724748823-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c3196713672854270451\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Luci</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1398894328583#c3196713672854270451\">30 avril, 2014 23:45</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Testée et c vraiment addictif c horrible surtout que c calorique mais dur dur de resister et d&#39;en prendre une autre part :) sinon moi j&#39;ai remplacer le rhum par de la fleur d&#39;oranger dans le gateau ainsi que glacage et c super bon jadore merci en tout cas</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3196713672854270451\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/3196713672854270451\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c3196713672854270451-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c3196713672854270451-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c3196713672854270451-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"3196713672854270451\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c3196713672854270451-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c5865738599255318972\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Laure G.</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1399744089583#c5865738599255318972\">10 mai, 2014 19:48</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Très très bon gâteau, je suis Nantaise et je ne l&#39;ai découvert que récemment ! Comme vous je ne mets pas tout le rhum car sinon je trouve cela trop prononcé.<br>Mais effectivement une fois qu&#39;on y goutte on ne peut plus se passer de le faire régulièrement :) En apparté, super votre blog, bravo ! en regardant votre blog on a envie de tester toutes vos recettes.</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5865738599255318972\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/5865738599255318972\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c5865738599255318972-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c5865738599255318972-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c5865738599255318972-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"5865738599255318972\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c5865738599255318972-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c219500550579147273\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Carob</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1400079243348#c219500550579147273\">14 mai, 2014 16:54</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour Valérie, <br><br>Juste pour info, je ne vois pas le gâteau nantais dans les recettes, j&#39;ai dû chercher pour retrouver la recette. J&#39;en ai déjà fait un dimanche, mais je l&#39;ai donné à des amis, je le refais donc aujourd&#39;hui pour le manger avec mon chéri ! </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"219500550579147273\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/219500550579147273\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c219500550579147273-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c219500550579147273-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c219500550579147273-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"219500550579147273\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c219500550579147273-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c6537950928404203376\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1401710793720#c6537950928404203376\">02 juin, 2014 14:06</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Je viens de prendre 2kg en une semaine de vacances et je tombe sur cette recette...aïe !<br>Je voulais me refaire des petits pains au Fjord et, comme souvent, je me suis baladée sur le reste du blog...je n&#39;aurais peut-être pas dû ! Le gâteau nantais est dans ma to-do list c&#39;est parti ;) et je pense que tu as raison d&#39;avoir diminué le rhum sinon ça doit l&#39;emporter sur le reste </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6537950928404203376\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/6537950928404203376\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c6537950928404203376-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c6537950928404203376-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c6537950928404203376-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"6537950928404203376\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c6537950928404203376-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c2699138616573148053\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1401995231348#c2699138616573148053\">05 juin, 2014 21:07</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Coucou Valérie, RE FAIT, RE DEVORE et (on en) RE DEMANDE !!! RE MERCI ;-)))) Myriam miam miam </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2699138616573148053\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/2699138616573148053\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c2699138616573148053-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c2699138616573148053-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c2699138616573148053-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"2699138616573148053\">Répondre</a></div></ol></div></div><div class=\"comment-replybox-single\" id=\"c2699138616573148053-ce\"></div></li><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c1365850150449057859\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//resources.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\">Anonyme</cite><span class=\"icon user \"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1403530445522#c1365850150449057859\">23 juin, 2014 15:34</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Bonjour, <br><br>je souhaiterais faire ce gâteau pour l&#39;anniversaire de ma fille et donc ne pas y mettre d&#39;alcool. Est ce possible? Je ne pense pas que ça change foncièrement la recette (sauf le goût de Rhum). Aussi pour le glaçage auriez vous une idée pour remplacer le rhum? <br><br>Merci par avance. <br><br>PS : votre blog est génial, j&#39;ai déjà fait 5 de vos recettes (sucrées et salées) et ma famille m&#39;en redemande!!! Continuez&#8230; :-)</p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><a class=\"comment-reply\" target=\"_self\" data-comment-id=\"1365850150449057859\">Répondre</a><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-96055870\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/1365850150449057859\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c1365850150449057859-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c1365850150449057859-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div><li class=\"comment\" id=\"c7616332509098579320\"><div class=\"avatar-image-container\"><img src=\"//4.bp.blogspot.com/-KKr4PU9mrtw/WDTAi1pyCYI/AAAAAAAAgmE/45r63wWTsbcMSW4f4n6O23fUcU4gxHKUgCK4B/s35/SMALL-BLACK.jpg\" alt=\"\"/></div><div class=\"comment-block\"><div class=\"comment-header\"><cite class=\"user\"><a href=\"https://www.blogger.com/profile/03779115722283638667\" rel=\"nofollow\">Valérie</a></cite><span class=\"icon user blog-author\"></span><span class=\"datetime secondary-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.cestmafournee.com/2014/03/le-gateau-nantais.html?showComment=1403558630471#c7616332509098579320\">23 juin, 2014 23:23</a></span></div><p class=\"comment-content\">Oui c&#39;est possible. Et pour le glaçage il faudra remplacer le rhum par l&#39;eau. </p><span class=\"comment-actions secondary-text\"><span class=\"item-control blog-admin blog-admin pid-881483793\"><a target=\"_self\" href=\"https://www.blogger.com/comment/delete/3933576376853880683/7616332509098579320\">Supprimer</a></span></span></div><div class=\"comment-replies\"><div id=\"c7616332509098579320-rt\" class=\"comment-thread inline-thread hidden\"><span class=\"thread-toggle thread-expanded\"><span class=\"thread-arrow\"></span><span class=\"thread-count\"><a target=\"_self\">Réponses</a></span></span><ol id=\"c7616332509098579320-ra\" class=\"thread-chrome thread-expanded\"><div></div><div id=\"c7616332509098579320-continue\" class=\"continue\"><a class=\"